name: MotorStorm Pacific Rift camp
desc: Unwind after a day of brutal racing in your beachfront campsite.

name: The Prairie Saloon
desc: Mosey on down to the Saloon for a rootin tootin good time. Put on a performance on the stage, ride around the expansive grounds, or tend to your horse. Includes  Horse care game with 7 in-game rewards 4 Exclusive Saloon rewards This space is a Clubhouse.

name: Pharaohs Tomb
desc: Loosely translated from the hieroglyphs  Here lies Pharaoh Homenkhammun, about whom dancers rejoice and upon whom the Eye of Horus lingers. Loved by all, may he find further glory in the West.

name: The Spunland Cottage
desc: Take up residence in the Spunland Cottage, with scenic views of the purple skies and hills of Spunland. Includes a garden area with a grazing Flusho Spunner, suitable for relaxing in the afternoon. Explore the maze in the darker depths of the cottage when the house Lumino Spunner permits access. Trigger Sonic Spunners for your own combination of soundtrack, or invite your friends over for a Score Challenge and start the Spun Clock  who can catch the most Rabbits, collect the most Fruit and find the most Eggs in the spun time limit? Become a spun home owner today.

name: Musicality Apartment
desc: A unique live music venue - up to four players can grab an instrument and jam compete against each other. Comes complete with the Dance music pack additional packs are available to purchase at the Musicality shop.

name: The Halloween Tour Bus Clubhouse
desc: The time has come to hit the road and party. Take full advantage of the freedoms a virtual world provides, slip the bus into cruise control and join the party at full speed. Just remember what goes on tour, stays on tour.

name: Discotheque Clubhouse
desc: Dance the night away in this stylish discotheque. Featuring animated disco balls, spotlights and lasers, this vast underground night-club even contains a rythm-action dance mini-game, with a high-score leaderboard. Scoring 100,000 points will give you an exclusive reward... Whether you prefer to challenge your friends at the mini-game, party on the animated illuminated dance floor, sit on the stools at the bar, or relax on the comfy armchairs, this is the perfect place to invite your friends.

name: Obsidian Officers Quarters
desc: Earth Fleet has constructed a new residency wing of the Novus Prime space station for high-ranking Obsidian pilots. Each apartment includes a Zero-Gravity Simulation System for the owner and guests.

name: Men in Black Headquarters
desc: Get an all-access pass when you own the Men In Black Headquarters as your own Private Space. Enjoy being the boss of the most top-secret organization established to monitor alien activity on Earth. Hang out with Frank the Pug in the MIB Offices, shop in the armory and relax in the break room. So suit up and get ready for the explosive return of Agents Kay and Jay in Men in Black III and the epic new video game Men in Black  Alien Crisis .

name: The Nightclub  Clubhouse
desc: The Nightclub is the perfect venue for a fantastic night out. Dance to pumping music tracks on the dance floor, sip on drinks in the lounge area, or activate the foam cannon for an extra crazy night. Please note, in order to access this Clubhouse you will need to have purchased the Clubhouse slot from either the Estates Store or the Clubs menu (available in Options).

name: A Dark Wizard s Mansion
desc: Who knows what Dark magic has been performed within these walls? This centuries-old stately home is the perfect residence for the aspiring Dark witch or wizard. Please be aware that only Pottermore furniture can be placed in Pottermore personal apartments and that all chat functions have been disabled. Pottermore furniture can be purchased from the Pottermore shop. #PMExtraCommerce

name: Glittering Sands Secluded Retreat
desc: Spend your holiday on a luxurious private beach. The clear blue sea, the white sandy beach, and the cottage on the ocean are all yours. With a friend, or with that special someone. Your holiday has just begun.

name: The Spunland Cottage
desc: Take up residence in the Spunland Cottage, with scenic views of the purple skies and hills of Spunland.

name: Xi  Continuum - Vertigo Apartment
desc: This fantastical outdoor apartment, situated on the side of a skyscraper overlooking the Continuum, defies belief. This apartment grows in size as you play through Xi  Continuum, resulting in a massive and amazing home.

name: Country Chic - Tour Bus
desc: The time has come to hit the road and party. Take full advantage of the freedoms a virtual world provides, slip the bus into cruise control and join the party at full speed. Just remember what goes on tour, stays on tour.

Featuring animated disco balls, spotlights and lasers, this vast underground night-club even contains a rythm-action dance mini-game, with a high-score leaderboard. Getting a high score will give you an exclusive reward... Whether you prefer to challenge your friends at the mini-game, party on the animated illuminated dance floor, sit on the stools at the bar, or relax on the comfy armchairs, this is the perfect place to invite your friends.

name: Audi Technology Apartment
desc: The Audi Technology Apartment is your reward for configuring and racing your perfect car in the Audi Technology Experience. Inside the apartment you can relax, entertain your friends, or simply admire the view of the city below.

name: Secret Peacekeeping Base, Yuma Caf
desc: At a glance it appears to be a tasteful coffee shop, but behind a door in the rear is a secret base for heroes that utilise the most advanced science to battle evil. Well then, lets defend our tranquil planet Earth from the clutches of evil.

name: My Private Hideaway
desc: Washed ashore on a solitary island in the south seas. The blazing sun, the quiet ocean, the refreshing breeze, crap. I built a house on top of a cliff and even forgot to go home. You are now able to go to the

name: The War Room Clubhouse
desc: The War Room - perfect for clan meetings, socialising and plotting world domination. You and your fellow warmongerers can have your face and commands displayed on large screens throughout this high tech facility.

name: Japanese Teahouse
desc: A remote mountain location, with abundant vegetation and water. A small teahouse stands past the gate, beyond the garden stepping stones.The confined teahouse built according to the principles of wabi and sabi allows one to draw near to visitors. Spend a brief moment in silence.

name: Moonlight Room
desc: When the sun sets, darkness reigns the night and only the magic of the moon lights up the streets. At that precise moment, the Moonlight Room comes to life. Its dark tones and silver trims are full with beauty, class and distinction. This is a shelter for lovers of the night.

name: LOOT s Space Apartment
desc: Enjoy the luxury of the future with this three-story apartment with loft. Experience the expansive views of Earth, space and the LOOT Space Station. Watch jellyfish swim in the two-story aquarium located in the center of the apartment. Relax in the aquatic meditation environment located on the bottom level. This wonderful personal space is also equipped with your own Space Apartment Remote Access (S.A.R.A.). With S.A.R.A. s help you can  View up to 5 different Twitter feeds on a news ticker Choose out of 8 screen locations to view your LOOT EOD Search for photos on FlickR and display them on any or all of the 16 photo screens available throughout the space. Each photo screen even lets you set-up slideshows. S.A.R.A. s also lets you control your environment with retractable ceiling, automated blinds and dynamic lighting options. In space, you couldn t ask for a better friend.

name: Acorn Meadows Park Apartment - 1st Birthday.
desc: Join us in in celebrating Acorn Meadows Parks 1st Birthday. Your own little private slice of Acorn Meadows Park, this lakeside garden apartment provides the perfect place to relax and take time away from the main Park without leaving the Acorn Meadows environment. Awarded in the 1st Birthday Acorn Meadows Park after completing all 22 Birthday Challanges.

name: Acorn Meadows Park Apartment - Winter
desc: Your own little private slice of Acorn Meadows Park, this lakeside garden apartment provides the perfect place to relax and take time away from the main Park without leaving the Acorn Meadows environment.

name: TOROs House
desc: A model of the 8-mat room TORO lived in in JapaneseMAINICHI ISSYO. Has a kitchen and bathroom.

name: The Sports Bar
desc: Spend time with your friends in this Sports-themed Bar, complete with Darts game. Exclusive to the VEEMEE 3D Printer.

name: Loco Island
desc: This personal space is your very own tropical island inhabited by LocoRoco characters. The tropical retreat is full of exciting activities. Collect berries that fall from the trees, and communicate with islanders to expand the facilities. Enjoy the Swing, Slide, Jukebox, and games for two players. And the more time you spend on Loco Island, the more vibrant and exciting the paradise becomes. Treat yourself to this fun-filled personal space.

name: Gothic Cathedral
desc: This ancient abandoned cathedral on the cliff is a sanctuary and a place you call home. From the majestic room, moonlit courtyard, to the massive candlelit hall, you can be the ruler of the night.

name: The Jam Jar Clubhouse
desc: The Jam Jar was established in the 1940 s as THE place to go. Discover the opulence and grandeur of this by gone era in a building rescued and restored to its rightful glory. Whether you decide to return it to its full boutique status, use its exquisite detail as a backdrop for a gallery or as the venue of the latest fashion event, The Jam Jar will still prove to be THE place to be seen.

name: Abbey Hill Cottage
desc: In a picturesque setting beside the river, stands the timeless Abbey Hill Cottage. Dating back to the 17th century, this period house was home to the Lord Ronald Phillipson distant cousin to the inventor of the watering can. The cottage now nestles in serenity, amongst stunning scenery, enveloped by a breathtaking countryside scene.

name: City of Flowers Penthouse Window to the World
desc: Make this apartment penthouse in downtown Paris yours, between the Eiffel Tower and the Arc de Triomphe. Your life in the city of flowers, Paris, begins here.

name: Nostalgic School Days
desc: Make the first floor of a school building yours, including two classrooms, a shop, and a hallway. The layout of desks, chairs, and other items is up to you. Make your own unique classroom and enjoy school life along with your friends. Be careful not to stay at school until late at night. You never know what might happen...

name: Nightlife Lounge Apartment
desc: Spend a night out on the town in your very own Nightlife Lounge. Inside, you can wine and dine your guests as they walk down the fashion runway inside. Get cozy and have a drink in the lounge area. Then spend the rest of the night on the lighted dance floor fist pumping to the DJ on the second floor. Are you ready to party?

name: Japanese Apartment
desc: A traditional Japanese apartment. Serene and tranquil.

name: Abbey Hill Cottage - Winter Retreat
desc: When winter descends, Abbey Hill takes on a new form of beauty. Revel in the stark white charm of the riverside cottage in the festive season. Escape from the cold in the fireside or explore the gardens to earn the 7 daily rewards on offer. If youre feeling really adventurous, why not go for a skate on the frozen surface of the river?

name: Red Bull House of Skate
desc: FOR SALE  Red Bull s 10,000 sq ft House of Skate including scenic views of the Hollywood Hills, steamy hot tub and a playable skate game. Flip, grind, and ollie your way through this modern skate haven while earning medals and street cred. Make it your own.

name: The Dream Yacht
desc: Have The Lifestyle You Always Dreamed Of With The Dream Yacht From Figment. Three Decks Of Opulent Living, Two Hot Tubs And More Than 20 Collectable Rewards, Plus An Exclusive Commerce Point Only Available Through The Dream Yacht. Live The Dream.

name: Luxury Train Apartment
desc: Sometimes you cant spend all day in your apartment as you have to head to important meetings and social events. Take a trip through a scenic environment whilst relaxing with your friends as the world outside passes you by.

name: Seasons-themed Room
desc: A Personal Space To Enjoy The Changing Seasons.

name: A House in Hogsmeade
desc: The only all-wizarding village in Britain, Hogsmeade is situated close to Hogwarts. The Hogwarts Express travels to and from the villages station. Please be aware that only Pottermore furniture can be placed in Pottermore personal apartments and that all chat functions have been disabled. Pottermore furniture can be purchased from the Pottermore shop. #PMExtraCommerce

name: Demonic Cutteridge Estate
desc: The abysmal darkness will imprison your soul for eternity.

name: The London Pub
desc: [Only for those above 18 years old. Please verify that you are 18 years of age or older to purchase.] Located in London, England, the pub comes with its own fantastic darts game and high score tables, working drink pumps and a bunch of hidden surprises and rewards. Cheers.

name: The Complex 2  Clubhouse
desc: This clubhouse, brought to you by nDreams, is based on the Complex 2 apartment. This luxurious cliff-side complex comes with all additional rooms and rewards already unlocked.

name: Meekum Industries Skylab

name: Hollywood Hills House Nighttime Estate (with Home Theater)
desc: Gaze upon glistening Los Angeles as Hollywood Hills royalty, in your private mansion above the LA skyline. Features include  Built-in Entertainment On Demand theatre system A swimming feature for the infinity pool. THIS is the spot to entertain your closest friends and clients. Purchase of this estate comes bundled with the LOOT Active Camera and Active Light, so you can film your parties and upload them to YouTube. PLEASE READ  Due to contractual and rights agreements, all content may not be available in all countries. Content availability is dependent on the geolocation of the device. CRACKLE content is only available in US, CA, UK, and AU. RADIOIO is only available in US and CA. Only one LOOT TV or LOOT Radio can be active at a time.

name: Infinite Oasis Ranch Clubhouse
desc: The perfect place for a mid-summer retreat, the Infinite Oasis Ranch has it all. From lively cacti and ageless palm trees to panoramic views of the surrounding mountain ridge, this space packs it all. The Infinite Oasis Ranch space is a clubhouse where everyone is invited to join.

name: Darlas Den
desc: This is our gift to you just for visiting The Midway. Admire your prowess on the prize runway, win access to the steamy hot tub, earn your entry into the Big Bang game, purchase a personal arcade shooter, and ultimately entertain Darla in the disco.

name: Crystal Seashores Clubhouse
desc: Crystal Seashores is a lavish waterfront home meant for those with extravagant lifestyles. A split staircase, open foyer, and backyard swimming pool are just footnotes when compared to the ocean view this home has to offer. The Crystal Seashores space is a clubhouse where everyone is invited to join.

name: The Dream Yacht
desc: Have the lifestyle you always dreamed of with the Dream Yacht from Figment. Three decks of opulent living, two hot tubs and more than 20 collectable rewards, plus an exclusive commerce point only available through the Dream Yacht. Live the dream.

name: Aurora-Champion-Apartment
desc: To reward you for your hard work and dedication to Aurora, we have gifted you this Aurora Champion apartment.

name: South Island retreat
desc: An isolated island in the South Sea, washed ashore. Shining sun, calm sea, fresh breeze, Oh no. I forgot to go home and built a house on a cliff ... The back door of the log cabin leads to the private garden of the Southern Island Hideaway lounge. This personal space will also have various elements added to it in the future.

desc: Throw a dance party in the great outdoors, a treetop pot-luck, or a swim party in the natural lagoon, the Dream Forest Paradise Clubhouse has plenty of room for up to 32 of you. As well as the unparalleled natural beauty youll find the usual exquisite architecture youve come to expect from Figment, and unique rewards too. Live the Dream.

name: Inferno Apartment
desc: Literally the hottest place to hang out in PlayStation Home. Amongst the fire and brimstone you will make your home, welcome to Hell.

name: Doctor Who TARDIS
desc: TARDIS stands for Time And Relative Dimension In Space. The TARDIS looks like a 1950 s wooden Police Phone Box on the outside, but is of infinite proportions on the inside. Amaze your friends when they discover the wonder of Time Lord technology. Doctor Who logo 2013 and TM BBC. Licensed by BBC WW Ltd.

name: Iron Fusion Vault (Male)
desc: Hidden in a top secret location, this Vault is filled with a collection of new suits from Iron Fusion, each with their own individual mechanics. The Iron Fusion Vault holds the secrets to metering out swift justice in PlayStation Home. Upon entering the Iron Fusion Vault, the owner will be awarded Mechjet Epic plus four special suits  Panthabot Bhaltair, Barrin Mech Suit, Mechjet Magnor and Mechsuit Pilot Diablo.

name: Summer Sunflowers In Bloom
desc: A Personal Space Where You Can Enjoy The Good Old Japanese Summer.

desc: Bowling Apartment SEO

The Nightlife Lounge is a clubhouse where everyone is invited to join.

name: Tree House Personal Apartment
desc: A stunning circular treehouse built around the trunk of an ancient tree high up in the mountains. Made of wood and circular in design, there are two levels each offering spectacular views of the waterfalls and mountains outside.

name: The Boutique Apartment  Clubhouse
desc: This Clubhouse from nDreams is the perfect place for the suave and sexy socialites of PlayStation Home - based on The Boutique Apartment. This luxury clubhouse comes with all the additional rooms already unlocked.

name: Rapture Metro Apartment
desc: From Sinclair Solutions, please enjoy your new apartment in Rapture. As a valued Sinclair Solutions tester, we know you need a place to relax after trying out our new products. Remember to explore the space and see all that Rapture has to offer.

name: Anime Style
desc: Anime fans, rejoice. A personal space for the otaku in all of us.

name: Summer House
desc: An exclusive retreat set amongst the mountains and lakes. A perfect place to relax and unwind.

name: The Prairie Ranch
desc: Git along little doggie. You cant call yourself a bona fide ranch owner until youve put your horse handling skills to the test. Groom and feed your horse the owners who take the best care of their horses are most richly rewarded. Includes  Horse care game with 7 in-game rewards 4 Exclusive Ranch rewards, 1 of which is also available to guests. This space is an Apartment.

name: Secret Base To Keep The Peace Yuma Cafe
desc: At First Glance, The Cafe Looks Quaint, But Behind The Door Is A Secret Base Where Heroes Fight Evil Using The Most Advanced Scientific Power. Now, You Must Protect The Peaceful Earth From The Hands Of Evil.

name: Dream Adventure
desc: Explore stunning tropical islands and discover hidden rewards aboard the Dream Adventure yacht. Leave the yacht on cruise and relax on the deck watching the world go by, or get active on the water craft or treasure hunting minigames. With 12 exclusive rewards.

name: PlayStation Home Mansion - First Floor
desc: Welcome to the PlayStation Home Mansion, an extravagant space filled with some of the rarest items around. On the first floor you ll find your mansion comes equipped with the best security money can buy  a live tiger. An Imperial staircase will lead you to the second floor while your kitchen comes fully stocked with gold appliances to fit your cooking needs and an adjacent dining room for you and your guests. Best of all, you ll be able to walk around while wearing your very own 100 % gold-virtual-thread lounge-wear that comes as a reward for purchasing the new space. And for an added bonus the PlayStation Home Mansion also allows for up to 5 gold rewards for each of your guests. Enjoy your time in the good life.

name: Ghostbusters Firehouse
desc: Own the Ghostbusters Firehouse HQ, a three floor personal space with ghost containment, garage office and living areas. Also included are a full-size Ecto-1, an interactive camera, a flying Slimer, PLUS exclusive furniture for your space.

name: Moonlight Space
desc: This is the personal space of peakvox ninja, Japanese lounge.

name: MyGym Apartment
desc: The luxurious MyGym apartment is perfect way to get in shape or relax after a hard day. Train your avatar on the built-in MyGym equipment  MyGym - Equipment - Weights Bench MyGym - Equipment - Stair Machine MyGym - Equipment - Cross Trainer MyGym - Equipment - Rowing Machine MyGym - Equipment - Running Machine MyGym - Equipment - Cycling Machine There are many ways to keep fit in the MyGym apartment, head to the weights room to build some muscle or find your centre in the yoga room. After your work out use the MySpa changing room to get into your swimming clothes then head to the sauna, hot tub or relax in the infinity pool with a beautiful view of the nearby tropical islands.

name: Masquerade Ball - The Ballroom
desc: The perfect personal space to host a lavish Masquerade Ball. Entertain your guests in this beautiful ballroom. Deck out your ballroom with the Masquerade Ball furniture range for extra authenticity.

name: Dolphy Room
desc: A relaxing virtual space where you can raise and interact with your own Dolphy.

name: Paris Clock Tower Apartment
desc: Take a European vacation without ever leaving your living room. Enjoy a beautiful Parisian vista from the luxury of your loft style apartment located in an old clock tower.

name: Paradise at Sea Clubhouse
desc: Explore the seven seas in style aboard the grandiose Paradise at Sea Clubhouse. With both a pool and hot tub located at the bow of the ship, you ll never tire of the soft summer rays giving you that perfect tan. Better yet, grab a drink at the bar inside and enjoy the day from the comfort of your own window side booth. The Paradise at Sea is a clubhouse where everyone is invited to join.

name: Blueprint  Home
desc: Blueprint  Home is an apartment that you can design, build and customise. You can tailor each aspect of your apartment including the walls, ceilings, floors, outer walls, windows, doorways, room sizes and positions, environment and skies, as well as place fantastic feature items in any rooms you like. Purchasing this apartment will give you access to the following content  n n * Blueprint  Home (Apartment) n * Blueprint  Home - Minimalist Style Pack n * Blueprint  Home - Classic Paint Style Pack n * Blueprint  Home - Idyllic Valley Environment n * Blueprint  Home - Paradise Island Environment n * Blueprint  Home - Blue Sky n * Blueprint  Home - Dusky Purple Sky n n All of the above items will become available in Blueprint  Home once purchased. Additional content sold separately.

name: Aurora Island

name: Crystal Seashores Apartment
desc: Crystal Seashores is a lavish waterfront home meant for those with extravagant lifestyles. A split staircase, open foyer, and backyard swimming pool are just footnotes when compared to the ocean view this home has to offer. Reward yourself and your friends with the exclusive Crystal Seashores Palm Tree, only available in the Crystal Seashores Apartment.

name: Cubic Residence
desc: Rooms on the north-west side of the flat, which resembles a cube, adjacent to the Home Square. The calm sea and soft sunlight below, and the calm room d cor with trees and stone, are a welcome break from the bustle of the square and will help you have a good time with your friends.

name: Post Apocalypse Apartment
desc: Part apartment, part fortress, this home will protect you from the hazards of the outside world.

name: Paradise at Sea Apartment
desc: Explore the seven seas in style aboard the grandiose Paradise at Sea Apartment. With both a pool and hot tub located at the bow of the ship, you ll never tire of the soft summer rays giving you that perfect tan. Better yet, grab a drink at the bar inside and enjoy the day from the comfort of your own window side booth.

desc: Have the lifestyle you always dreamed of with the Dream Yacht from Figment. Three decks of opulent living, two hot tubs and 10 collectable rewards, plus an exclusive commerce point only available through the Dream Yacht. Live the dream.

name: Silicon Lounge
desc: This magical party space is the perfect solution to all your entertaining needs. Set in a secret desert location, the Silicon Lounge contains everything you need to host parties the likes of which PlayStation Home has never seen. Make a statement in this neon paradise, show off your moves on the interactive animated hexagonal dance floor or surprise your friends with luxurious gifts from the integrated Lockwood Gift Machine. And when you re all partied out, relax in the space s hidden underground chill-out snug if you can find it that is.

name: The Ranch House
desc: Welcome to your very own ranch where the sun never sets. This huge plot of land comes with an open paddock, a peaceful pond, a spacious house for you to rest at after a long day at Red Rock Springs.

name: Dream Island Clubhouse
desc: Live the life you always dreamed of with Dream Island from Figment. Your very own secluded tropical island hideaway. Swim in the ocean, find the hidden cave and discover the islands vibrant wildlife to obtain rewards. Invite friends to visit you at the islands impressive condo or host a barbecue on your private pier. Live the dream.

name: Dream Hideaway Clubhouse
desc: Enjoy the splendour of this exquisite woodland hideaway and relax in the luxurious surroundings . Youll also be able to collect 8 exclusive reward items, so why not treat yourself today?

name: Penthouse In The City Of Flowers -From The Window Of The World-
desc: Your Apartment Penthouse Is Located In The City Center Of Paris, Almost In The Center Of The Eiffel Tower And Arc De Triomphe. Life In Paris, The City Of Flowers, Starts Here.

name: The Windmill Apartment
desc: The Windmill Apartment from nDreams is the perfect picturesque setting if you enjoy peace and quiet. Surrounded by green fields and great views from the top of the windmill, this is the perfect home away from home in PlayStation Home.

name: Dream Island
desc: Live the life you always dreamed of with Dream Island from Figment. Your very own secluded tropical island hideaway. Swim in the ocean, find the hidden cave and discover the islands vibrant wildlife to obtain rewards. Invite friends to visit you at the islands impressive condo or host a barbecue on your private pier. Live the dream.

name: French Chateau Apartment
desc: Enjoy the summer in your new French Chateau. This stunning Chateau has a giant foyer and balcony, where you can bask in the light from your chandelier. But the real jewel is out back. Take a leisurely stroll in the courtyard, complete with perfectly manicured trees and bushes. All this natural beauty may inspire you to hang up some new art in your not so humble abode. Reward your guests with a French Chateau Painting, exclusive to the French Chateau personal space.

name: The Dragons Lair
desc: Youve conquered the dragon so why not take up his lair as your own? The Dragons Lair is the perfect place to host your friends, show off your rewards or simply relax with your riches surrounding you.

Enveloped by beautiful scenery, it is the perfect place for meditation - allowing visitors to achieve inner peace and clarity of mind. Some even say that when mastering the art of meditation, one can gain power over the seasons.

name: Blasters Bay
desc: The notoriously addictive TankTop shooter is back in this awesome private bay. Now you can gift this epic personal space so your friends can blast their way to high scores amongst the palm trees, looming rock formations and stunning waterfalls, as well as unlock 10 exclusive rewards.

Featuring animated disco balls, spotlights and lasers, this vast underground night-club even contains a rythm-action dance mini-game, with a high-score leaderboard. Scoring 100,000 points will give you an exclusive reward... Whether you prefer to challenge your friends at the mini-game, party on the animated illuminated dance floor, sit on the stools at the bar, or relax on the comfy armchairs, this is the perfect place to invite your friends.

name: Assassins Creed Personal Space
desc: This 15th Century Italian Renaissance-style Mansion Is Where Culture And Art Were Born. Enjoy The Beauty Of Venices Canals From The Windows Of This Beautifully Decorated Interior, Furnished With Your Choice Of Furnishings.

name: Eden - Primarchs Vigilarium
desc: Personal space that recreates the Primarchs Vigilarium from FINAL FANTASY XIII. 2009, 2010 SQUARE ENIX CO., LTD. All Rights Reserved. CHARACTER DESIGN  TETSUYA NOMURA

name: PetrolHead Apartment
desc: Like cars? Like workshops? Want to live in a workshop full of cars? Then this PetrolHead apartment is the place for you...

name: Original Home Square Apartment
desc: Take a stroll down memory lane, take a left at nostalgia avenue and youll find yourself in the original Home Square.

name: SFRGBT.. Tropical Island
desc: Enjoy a penalty shoot-out against the worlds greatest robot goalkeeper on your very own tropical island at dusk. In addition to the SFRGBT.. minigame, the island comes complete with beach shelter, roaring fire and a boat to take you home again. The minigame also includes 4 unique reward items (sand castle, bucket and spade, Mr. Wilson face ball and shark fin wearable accessory) which can only be won by playing against robo-goalie in this exclusive Personal Space.

name: Twingate Castle - Apartment
desc: Every story has two sides, every day has its night and every soul has its dark side. What would happen if these two sides were ever parted, if magic entered the roots of your soul and divided it into two? The curse hung in the air filling every corner of the castle. The splitting of a soul in two, one side to hold all that was good, great and beautiful, the other half to be filled with the darkness of evil, bitterness and hatred. Here everything is light, the feeling of hope and happiness is palpable. But this is Twingate Castle...

name: Hollyridge Estate
desc: The Hollyridge Estate is the perfect setting for an elegant winter soiree. This personal space features classic Victorian architecture and design and also features built-in decorating options which allow you to create a festive atmosphere without taking up any furniture slots. Includes customizable wallpaper, a snowball fight minigame and much more.

name: Personal Casino Apartment
desc: Your very own casino right on the strip. Treat your friends to a night of fun and games. Here, you are your own casino boss. Whatever you say goes.

name: Palace of the Seven Winds
desc: Reign over your own celestial paradise with the Palace of the Seven Winds. Exert your influence over the heavens themselves to alter time, break free of your earthly shackles and take to the skies, lounge in your own personal harem-style apartments, have wishes granted by your personal genie, unlock rewards and much more.

name: Mount Olympus
desc: Lounge like the gods as you sit atop the clouds in your very own Mt. Olympus. Take your rightful place on the throne, overlooking your impluvium (a water basin for you mortals). Take a stroll out back in your peristylium to catch some sun. Make sure to have one of your worshippers pull up your chariot for you when you leave. Reward your guests with a Mount Olympus Bolts (Male or Female), exclusive to the Mount Olympus personal space.

name: GZ Burger
desc: GZ Burger, a hamburger shop neighboring a large lake, is all yours. The interior layout of the tables, chairs, etc. is up to your imagination. Create your own unique restaurant and invite your friends.

name: Edo Nagaya
desc: This Personal Space Recreates A Backstreet Housing Complex In Edo, A Town Full Of Humanity. If You Have This Personal Space, You Can Use The Tenement House In The Lounge Oedo  Exterminating Mononoke As A Recovery Base.

name: Underwater Apartment
desc: Its wet out there.

name: The Sky Temple of Fratos
desc: Hail Fratos, may his spirit forever soar as freely as his temple in the sky.

name: The Complex 2
desc: This FREE apartment is brought to you by nDreams. Expand your complex by getting any or all of the additional rooms. In doing so, you wont only impress your friends with a great apartment but you will be rewarded for your efforts.

name: The Lost Dam Hideout
desc: Miles from civilisation and hidden deep in a gorge, this long-lost Dam is the perfect hideout for every aspiring evil overlord. The dark interior and bare rock set the mood and the Piranha pool adds a suitable finishing touch.

name: Savage Manor
desc: Enter if you dare. This tormented manor is steeped in grim history, history that will not remain in the past. Explore this mysterious apartment, but beware of the dangers that lurk within. Can you solve the cryptic riddles and learn the horrible truths ingrained within the structures living, breathing walls?

name: Glittering Sands Secluded Retreat
desc: Spend your holiday on a luxurious private beach. The clear blue sea, the white sandy beach, and the cottage on the ocean are all yours. With a friend, or with that special someone. Your holiday has just begun.

name: Tearoom, Silver Monastery
desc: The luxurious and gorgeous silver tearoom.Among the trees one can see a sparkling silver figure, said to take your breath away. In this mountain region far removed from civilization, you can spend some time with a cup of tea, cut off from everyday life. * A present from GZ Gift

name: Assassin s Creed Apartment
desc: Take time out and relax in the birthplace of culture and art, 15th Century Italy. Place your treasured possessions within a luxurious Venice apartment overlooking the famous canals.

name: Carla s Coffee Shop Apartment
desc: Carlas Coffee Shop is located in the heart of the City and is the perfect place to catch up with old friends. With street areas and the coffee shop to decorate you can make this apartment your own.

name: Santorini Greece
desc: Make a virtual journey to the cradle of western civilization and visit the archipelago off Greeces mainland. Here youll live in a lush apartment with spectacular views of the ocean and surrounding city. Ya ssou.

name: My Secret Villa on a Blue Whale
desc: Take a trip through the ocean on the back of a whale. Visit tropical countries, the Mediterranean, and even the northern fjords. It s up to you where you steer the gentle giant as you enjoy this relaxing cruise.

name: Go Fish Tropical Island
desc: Now you can catch fish all day with the Go Fish Tropical Island. This private island gives you access to all the fishing you could ever want, along with your own beach to relax on.

name: Blasters Paradise - Sodium Personal Space
desc: Blast your way to an epic score with the awesome TankTop shooter in this stunning sub-tropical personal space. With spectacular waterfalls, a mysterious abandoned mill, and the addictive TankTop shooter, this waterside hang-out will be the envy of all your friends.

name: The Aurora Chinatown Apartment
desc: Welcome to Chinatown - a cool new apartment space from nDreams. Hang out in Chinatown Square, or shelter from the rain in the surrounding building.

name: MotorStorm Monument Valley Camp
desc: Take time out from all the racing and partying to enjoy the festival from afar in your mesa-top campsite.

name: French Chateau Apartment
desc: Enjoy the summer in your new French Chateau. This stunning Chateau has a giant foyer and balcony, where you can bask in the light from your chandelier. But the real jewel is out back. Take a leisurely stroll in the courtyard, complete with perfectly manicured trees and bushes. All this natural beauty may inspire you to hang up some new art in your not so humble abode. Reward your guests with a French Chateau Painting, exclusive to the French Chateau personal space.

name: Novus Prime Officers Quarters
desc: These large private suites are normally reserved for high-ranking officers of the Earth Fleet. Civilians and pilots alike may now claim their own piece of the Novus Prime space station, at least until these suites run out. Space is available to install your own hangar for your fighter ships, which allows you to play missions with your guests. You may also install a Zero-gravity Simulation system, which allows occupants to safely float about the quarters.

name: GZ Burger
desc: GZ Burger, a hamburger shop neighbouring a large lake, is all yours. The interior layout of the tables, chairs, etc. is up to your imagination. Create your own unique restaurant and invite your friends.

name: Hollywood Hills House Daytime Estate (with Home Theater)
desc: Live like a celebrity with a mansion in the Hollywood Hills, set above the LA skyline. Invite your friends into your home theater for a social viewing experience with videos, trailers and exclusive content from Sony Pictures. Features include  Built-in Entertainment On Demand theater system A swimming feature for the infinity pool. THIS is the estate to own if you want to relax in the lap of luxury with your friends. Purchase of this estate comes bundled with the LOOT Active Camera and Active Light, so you can film your parties and upload them to YouTube at no extra cost. PLEASE READ  Due to contractual and rights agreements, all content may not be available in all countries. Content availability is dependent on the geolocation of the device. CRACKLE content is only available in US, CA, UK, and AU. RADIOIO is only available in US and CA. Only one LOOT TV or LOOT Radio can be active at a time.

name: Iron Fusion Vault (Female)
desc: Hidden in a top secret location, this Vault is filled with a collection of new suits from Iron Fusion, each with their own individual mechanics. The Iron Fusion Vault holds the secrets to metering out swift justice in PlayStation Home. Upon entering the Iron Fusion Vault, the owner will be awarded Mechjet Glory plus four special suits  Panthabot Teigra, Mechjet Ferruma, Mechjet Ragnara and Mechsuit-Pilot Necra.

name: Rock Reveller Tour Bus
desc: The time has come to hit the road and party. Take full advantage of the freedoms a virtual world provides, slip the bus into cruise control and join the party at full speed. Just remember what goes on tour, stays on tour.

name: Yutakanapa-sonaruteien
desc: Additional Personal Gardens In The Palais Region. More Gardening Plans Are Available, Giving You More Freedom To Plant Your Planters. The Images Are Gardening Examples.

name: Relaxing Edo Bathhouse
desc: A relaxing atmosphere for body and soul. Invite a friend, take a soak together in the soothing waters, and watch the days fatigue melt away.

name: My Private Hideaway
desc: Washed ashore on a solitary island in the south seas. The blazing sun, the quiet ocean, the refreshing breeze, crap. I built a house on top of a cliff and even forgot to go home. You are now able to go to the Southern Island Hideaway lounge from the back door of the loghouse. Also, there are plans to add many different things to this personal space in the future.

name: Chamber Apartment
desc: For a limited time only get the exclusive Chamber apartment for Home. This apartment blends the real and surreal with fire-pits, waterfalls, and even a mysterious giant tree in the center that seems to come alive when walking by.

name: Onlong Apartment No.2 Sukimasou
desc: Quadruple Room, No Bath, Shared Toilet. The Property Is Conveniently Located Near The Downtown Area.

name: SFRGBT.. Tropical Island
desc: Enjoy a penalty shoot-out against the worlds greatest robot goalkeeper on your very own tropical island at dusk. In addition to the SFRGBT.. minigame, the island comes complete with beach shelter, roaring fire and a boat to take you home again. The minigame also includes 4 unique reward items (sand castle, bucket and spade, Mr. Wilson face ball and shark fin wearable accessory) which can only be won by playing against robo-goalie in this exclusive Personal Space.

name: Acorn Meadows Park Apartment - Dusk
desc: Your own little private slice of Acorn Meadows Park, this lakeside garden apartment provides the perfect place to relax and take time away from the main Park without leaving the Acorn Meadows environment.

name: Bonk Living Space
desc: A personal space built in the primitive age of Bonk. Light up the room with Primitive Light, and liven things up with Primitive Furniture like what can be found in the river.* Primitive Furniture can only be used in this personal space.

name: Gnome Curling Secret Garden
desc: Enjoy Gnome Curling in the privacy of your own secret garden. Comes complete with a gazebo, beautiful floral displays and a magical door to take you back home again.

name: The Space Station Clubhouse
desc: The Space Station needs a crew, and youve been selected to take part in an all new out-of-this-world experience. Your Space Station adventure will have you defending your new home against incoming asteroids in the fully interactive Station Defense turret center. On top of defending the station your tasks will also include lowering and raising the external shutters so you dont get blinded by the sun and youll even have to evacuate the garbage you produce in to the vaccum of space. Your shuttle is cleared for arrival. The Space Station space is a clubhouse where everyone is invited to join.

name: Castle Strakh
desc: For centuries, Castle Strakh has been the subject of tales and superstition amongst the local people. Some say the castle is haunted by the ghostly bride of Count Strakh, others that it hides a secret lab used for horrific experiments. Do you dare seek out the truth? Contains 11 ghastly rewards and LKWD Life XP.

name: Creek Falls
desc: Hidden deep within the forest, Creek Falls sits at the bed of a stunning waterfall. The home is built like a modern day studio with a living room and bedroom packed into one large open space. You can even hang out with friends in your outdoor patio and breathe in the soft chilly wind of the autumn air. Reward yourself and your friends with an exclusive Animated Autumn Tree furniture items, only available in Creek Falls.

name: Luxury Lighthouse Apartment
desc: The nDreams Luxury Lighthouse apartment is spread across multiple floors and comes complete with authentic rotating light effect. Situated on a picturesque cliffside this is the perfect get away.

name: Mystery Key - (#3 of 3)
desc: This Mystery Key is only for the most sophisticated Home user. Collect all three.

name: Tycoon Penthouse
desc: Take your living experience to new heights with the Tycoon Penthouse, perched high above the city sky. The window-walled space comes with your own private helipad, an aquarium that reaches from floor to ceiling, and a spiralling staircase that gives the space its modern design. Dare to defy gravity and add this little slice of heaven to your collection today.

name: Castle Greywold  Apartment
desc: In this new apartment, you can take up arms in the training yard, entertain guests in the audience chamber, or survey your surroundings from the castle ramparts.

name: Zombie DeadQuarters
desc: If we Zombies have offended, think but this, and all is mended, that you have but slumberd here, while these corpses did appear.

name: The Nightmare Yacht
desc: The Dream has become a Nightmare. This once opulent yacht has gone to wrack and ruin. Experience the eerie surroundings for yourself and discover some wicked rewards. Board this cursed vessel at your own peril, you have been warned

name: Snow Globe Clubhouse
desc: Ever shook a snow globe and gazed inside wanting to be a part of that magical, miniature world? Now this can be a virtual reality with our Snow Globe Clubhouse, set on a table inside The Jam Jar, the outside world is visible and giant. Live the magic and feel the snow because after all .. There s Snow Place like PlayStation Home.

name: Dream Hideaway
desc: Gift this and let them rest and relax in the luxury they have become accustomed to.

name: The Haven of the Skies Clubhouse
desc: The Haven of the Skies Clubhouse is a breathtaking twilit environment full of secrets, intrigue and adventure. Taking to the skies on your magic carpet, collect the Gems that your Genie demands so that he may grant your wishes.

name: LKWDvenue
desc: The Perfect Location For Social Events. Create The Ultimate Event At LKWD Venues. Interactive Points Of Interest With Unique Animations, Options To Customize The Venues, And Mini-games To Play.

name: Hollywood Hills House Nighttime Clubhouse (with Home Theatre)
desc: Entertain like an industry mogul in this ultimate clubhouse, set in the Hollywood Hills above the LA skyline. Invite your friends into your home theater for a social viewing experience with videos, trailers and exclusive content from Sony Pictures. Features include  Built-in Entertainment On Demand theater system A swimming feature for the infinity pool. THIS is where the party is for you and your club. Purchase of this clubhouse comes bundled with the LOOT Active Camera and Active Light, so you can film your parties and upload them to YouTube at no extra cost. PLEASE READ  Due to contractual and rights agreements, all content may not be available in all countries. Content availability is dependent on the geolocation of the device. CRACKLE content is only available in US, CA, UK, and AU. RADIOIO is only available in US and CA. Only one LOOT TV or LOOT Radio can be active at a time.

name: All Spaces SeaClyff
desc: You save big by getting both the Retreat and the Clubhouse for one price. * SeaClyff Retreat * SeaClyff Clubhouse * Pulp Music Radio

name: Musicality Club House
desc: A unique live music venue perfect for hosting club gatherings. Up to four players can grab an instrument and jam compete against other club members. Comes complete with all music packs - Dance, Rock and RnB. Please note, in order to access this Club House you will need to have purchased the Club House slot from either the Estates Store or the Clubs menu (available in Options).

name: 921 Acacia Drive
desc: Live the suburban dream at 921 Acacia Drive. With a range of rooms for you to decorate to suit your tastes, along with 8 daily reward items that give you the essential furniture items, this personal space is a bonafide slice of Americana.

name: Dolphy Room
desc: A Private Space Floating In Virtual Space. It Is Equipped With A Function For Raising A Virtual Pet Dolphy. Spend A Healing Time With Dolphy.

name: Mystery Key - (#1 of 3)
desc: This Mystery Key will help complete your luxury Mansion. Collect all three.

name: PlayStation Home Mansion - Infinity Pool
desc: Boasting a generous outdoor patio, this lavish waterfront backyard comes complete with two fireplaces, a marble bar, and gold statues overlooking your own private wishing fountain. Combine this with a large, glass-walled, infinity pool that looks out into the ocean s horizon and you have the perfect backyard for any social get-together or simply a relaxing afternoon. And for an added bonus the PlayStation Home Mansion also includes up to 5 unique gold rewards for each of your guests.

name: Rooftop Terrace - Apartment
desc: What better place than a rooftop terrace to host a social gathering. Impress your friends with the beautiful view of a bustling city at night.

name: Snow Globe Apartment
desc: Ever shook a snow globe and gazed inside wanting to be a part of that magical, miniature world? Now this can be a virtual reality with our Snow Globe Apartment, set on a table inside The Jam Jar, the outside world is visible and giant. Live the magic and feel the snow because after all .. There s Snow Place like PlayStation Home.

name: Fossil Museum
desc: In this personal space, the fossils that you found in the Southern Island Hideaway lounge are exhibited.

name: The Irish Pub
desc: A special St. Patricks Day themed version of the London pub, complete with Darts game, so you can enjoy good times and great craic with your friends.

name: Island Bungalow Clubhouse
desc: Nestled on the edge of a tropical paradise, this exquisite Island Bungalow is hidden somewhere on an uncharted coastline. Be the first to explore this mysterious paradise. The Island Bungalow space is a clubhouse where everyone is invited to join.

name: Pirate Galleon Apartment
desc: Moored By A Tropical Island, This Ship Comes Complete With Playable Cannon Mini-game And Four Pirate Themed Furniture Rewards. A Very Desirable Residence That Has Suddenly Become Available, Due To The Imprisonment Of The Previous Owner.

name: Stately Home Clubhouse (Gothic)
desc: The Stately Home (Gothic) is the perfect Clubhouse for those people who like the finer things in life with a slightly darker twist. With its large and beautiful grounds and a direct link through to the Masquerade Ball - The Ballroom (Gothic) Clubhouse, this space is a must-have. Also comes with five free rewards.

name: Raven Barracks
desc: Located in an equatorial rain forest, the Raven barracks is your little slice of paradise. You ll enjoy the ancient ruins, native birds, and beautiful flora fortified by composite fiber barricades, a seismic sensor grid and your elite Raven sentry detachment.

name: Sunlit Meadow
desc: This dappled glade is the ultimate chilled out place to relax and unwind surrounded by nature. Its the gift of tranquility.

name: Audi S1 Sledge Multiplayer
desc: Jump onto an Audi S1 Sledge and race down the mountainside against up to 5 other players, with a chance to win rewards.

name: The Casino  Keys to the VIP
desc: Please enjoy your stay at Paradise Springs. Compliments of the manager.

name: Twingate Castle - Clubhouse
desc: Every story has two sides, every day has its night and every soul has its dark side. What would happen if these two sides were ever parted, if magic entered the roots of your soul and divided it into two? The curse hung in the air filling every corner of the castle. The splitting of a soul in two, one side to hold all that was good, great and beautiful, the other half to be filled with the darkness of evil, bitterness and hatred. Here everything is light, the feeling of hope and happiness is palpable. But this is Twingate Castle...

name: The Jam Jar Apartment
desc: The Jam Jar was established in the 1940 s as THE place to go. Discover the opulence and grandeur of this by gone era in a building rescued and restored to its rightful glory. Whether you decide to return it to its full boutique status, use its exquisite detail as a backdrop for a gallery or as the venue of the latest fashion event, The Jam Jar will still prove to be THE place to be seen.

name: The War Room Clubhouse
desc: The War Room - Perfect For Clan Meetings, Socialising And Plotting World Domination. You And Your Fellow Warmongerers Can Have Your Face And Commands Displayed On Large Screens Throughout This High Tech Facility.

name: Edo Row Houses
desc: This personal space re-creates the collective residences on the back streets in the humantiy-overflowing Edo period. If you own this personal space, you can use Operation  Defend Edo Row Houses as a recovery spot.

name: Go Fish Tropical Island
desc: Now you can catch fish all day with the Go Fish Tropical Island. This private island gives you access to all the fishing you could ever want, along with your own beach to relax on.

name: Cutteridge Estate Clubhouse
desc: Unlock the mysteries of Cutteridge Estate. This elegant Victorian estate is rumored to be the final resting place of many dark and depraved souls. Do you dare to venture into these forsaken halls in search of the secrets which lie within?

name: Xi  Continuum - Standalone Vertigo Apartment
desc: This massive and fantastical outdoor apartment, situated on the side of a skyscraper overlooking a futuristic city, defies belief. Note  For only a small amount extra, purchase the Xi  Continuum - Axiom Agent Pack in the nDreams shop and obtain the game version of this apartment and access to Xi  Continuum, the exciting PlayStation Home adventure game featuring an evolving story, playable missions, and rewards.

name: LOOT s Sunset Yacht (With Home Theater)
desc: Watch live events, videos, podcasts and exclusive content in your luxurious on-board theater while cruising along in a beautiful tropical lagoon. In addition, this upgraded Amaterasu yacht now offers the ability to set the mood of your cruise. Sunrise, sunset, day, night? Its your choice. Thrill to breathtaking views and host exclusive parties, or sit back and count the stars under the romantic moonlight.

name: Lakeside Log Cabin
desc: Admire the stunning sunset across a mountain lake from this modern log cabin. The residence provides two large living areas with beautiful fire places in each and exquisite lighting throughout. These are elegantly joined by a large decked area that takes you right up to the lake side. Simply spectacular.

name: Visari Throne Room
desc: Personal apartment using the interior design of the throne room in Visari s palace.

name: Discotheque Club-house
desc: Dance the night away in this stylish discotheque. Featuring animated disco balls, spotlights and lasers, this vast underground night-club even contains a rythm-action dance mini-game, with a high-score leaderboard. Getting a high score will give you an exclusive reward... Whether you prefer to challenge your friends at the mini-game, party on the animated illuminated dance floor, sit on the stools at the bar, or relax on the comfy armchairs, this is the perfect place to invite your friends.

name: LittleBigPlanet Pod Penthouse
desc: Your very own LittleBigPlanet Pod Penthouse. Pod is crafted from the finest cardboard and the view is simply out of this world.

name: Las Vegas Suite
desc: This luxurious multilevel suite overlooks the endless hustle and bustle of the Las Vegas strip. From million dollar views of Sin Citys sprawling lights to extravagant amenities like the romantic rooftop hot tub, this magnificent residence is a must-have property for PlayStation Home high-rollers.

name: Ajagaras Peak
desc: Nestled atop a steep and perilous mountain Ajagaras Peak is only accessible to a select few - those known as the Dragon Scouts. A place for diligent training, scholarly pursuits and deep meditation the monastery at Ajagaras Peak was founded to train an elite band of soldiers who keep watch over the kingdom of Ajagara. With 7 daily rewards and the chance to catch a glimpse of a tame dragon, this truly is a unique personal space.

name: Moon Hermitage
desc: Peakvox Ninja This Personal Space Is Based On A Japanese Style Lounge. Owners Of This Hermitage Will Always Receive A 50% Increase In Login Bonuses In This Lounge. Placing The Following Furniture Sets (or Just Possessing Them) Will Further Increase The Login Bonus 25% Additional...Purchasers Of Decorative Japanese Furniture Sets 25% Additional...Purchasers Of Partition Japanese Furniture Sets 20% Additional...Purchasers Of Garden Set (pine) 20% Additional...Purchasers Of Garden Set (bamboo) 30% Additional ...10% Additional For Purchasers Of Garden Stone Sets...10% Additional For Purchasers Of Coolness Set 1...10% Additional For Purchasers Of Coolness Set 2...10% Additional For Purchasers Of Coolness Set 3 Visits To The Peakvox Ninja Lounge And The Benefits Of The Benefits Are Available To Those Who Are 17 Years Of Age Or Older. This Personal Space Can Be Used As A Regular Personal Space By Those Under 17 Years Old.

name: Avalon Keep  Clubhouse
desc: The wonderous Avalon Keep is now an expansive Clubhouse. Invite your friends to enjoy this space with all the same features as the personal space. Any upgrades you purchase for the Avalon Keep will also be reflected in the Clubhouse and vice versa. The Avalon Keep is an impregnable fortress on your very own floating island. The magical crystals of Avalon allow the landmass to stay afloat and power all the new technological advances that have swept the world of Avalon. Your Keep sets you apart as one of the nobility that have taken residence in the skies around Avalon. Master all the mini-games and share the wealth with the latest in gift machine technology. Can you unlock all the secrets of your Keep? - Dragonfly Automaton - Gift Machine for owners and guests - Scavenger Hunts for owners and guests - Interactive NPCs - Crystal Hunter Mini-game - Diurnal Controls

name: Loco Island
desc: This personal space is your very own tropical island inhabited by LocoRoco characters. The tropical retreat is full of exciting activities. Collect berries that fall from the trees, and communicate with islanders to expand the facilities. Enjoy the Swing, Slide, Jukebox, and games for two players. And the more time you spend on Loco Island, the more vibrant and exciting the paradise becomes. Treat yourself to this fun-filled personal space.

name: Joes Boxing Gym Apartment
desc: Joes Boxing Gym is the perfect place to hang out if you want to work on your moves and learn how to spit sawdust.

name: Bramblenook Farm
desc: Relax and get back to nature in this charming country farm. In this space you can raise plants and animals to improve your farming skills. As you gain experience, you will be able to plant new crops and raise new animals. Chop wood and level your woodworking skills to create furnishings for yourself or to gift to a guest. Place crafted furniture items in Bramblenook Farm for no furniture cost.

name: Japanese Garden Apartment
desc: Japanese Garden Apartment

name: Virtua Tennis 4 Baseline Battle
desc: A Virtua Tennis Court Game. Stop the robots.

name: The Midnight Glade
desc: A secluded glade under a moonlit starry sky. Gather around the solitary tree and warm yourself by the glow of the fire. Its the perfect place for a fireworks party.

name: Halloween Tour Bus
desc: The time has come to hit the road and party. Take full advantage of the freedoms a virtual world provides, slip the bus into cruise control and join the party at full speed. Just remember what goes on tour, stays on tour.

name: Dream Forest Paradise
desc: Your dreams come true with this breathtaking deluxe home amongst the trees, a luxurious treehouse if you will. Traverse the treetop bridges, swim in the lagoon, and explore your lush surroundings to obtain rewards. With a magnificent view from every angle youll never want to leave the Dream Forest Paradise from Figment. Live the Dream.

name: Acorn Meadows Park Apartment - Rainy Day
desc: Your own little private slice of Acorn Meadows Park, this lakeside garden apartment provides the perfect place to relax and take time away from the main Park without leaving the Acorn Meadows environment.

name: LKWD Venue
desc: The perfect location for all your social events, the Venue includes  Interaction points allowing you and your friends to utilise unique animations In depth customization options including optional features like the Stage and the Catwalk A voting minigame Your own personal LKWD Store An integrated Lockwood Gift Machine LKWD Venue Customisation Pack - Lockwood LKWD Venue Customisation Pack - Hive Be the ultimate host with the LKWD Venue.

name: Seasons-themed room
desc: A personal space to enjoy the changing seasons.

name: Enterprise-D Main Bridge with attached Captains Ready Room
desc: Hey Trekkers, The Star Trek Enterprise-D has come to PlayStation Home. You can now get yourself the official Main Bridge with the attached Captains Ready Room. TM and 2013 CBS Studios Inc. STAR TREK and all related marks and logos are trademarks of CBS Studios Inc. All Rights Reserved.

name: Desert Haven
desc: Take a minute and unwind at the charming Desert Haven clubhouse. Catch a couple sun-rays poolside while socializing with friends or meeting new ones. Take a nap beneath the cabanas or even catch a fireside chat next to the bonfires. The Desert Haven space is a clubhouse where everyone is invited to join.

name: Andys Room
desc: Experience life at a toy s eye view in Andy s room from Disney Pixar s Toy Story 3.

name: Living Room Stage Set from Loot
desc: The Living Room Stage Set provides Home users the opportunity to shout lights, camera, action. while collaborating with their friends to bring their own movies and television shows to life. The product comes with working lights and cameras, as well as props and backdrops. Additionally, the owner has the option to use any items that they already have purchased in Home while in the Stage Set. The Living Room Stage Set is the first of many Stage Sets coming from your friends at Loot .

name: The Drey VIP Room (For Male)
desc: You have been cordially invited to be a member of the Drey VIP Room. Take an exclusive look into the inspired fashions of Dreys celebrated designers. The Drey VIP Room features a stunning collection of old and new - everything to satisfy the hunger of the fashion elite worldwide. This includes 20 existing Gift Machine clothing items and 9 exclusive new clothing items.

name: Moonlight Space
desc: This is the peakvox ninja personal space, Japanese lounge.

name: Wizards Den
desc: Step into the Wizards Den where the magic and wonderment of an age long past still remains. Be mindful of the Dragons.

name: Hillside Apartment
desc: Built with a view in mind, the Hillside Apartment is the place to get away from the confines of a concrete jungle and bask in the luxury of a home away from home.

name: UFC Personal Space
desc: In the UFC Personal Space you get your own home gym. Earn points to spend in the UFC Octagon to win prizes.

name: Club Luminosity - Club House
desc: This is the ultimate place to share your love of neon. If you love things that glow, then this place is for you.

name: Secret Peacekeeping Base, Yuma Caf
desc: At a glance it appears to be a tasteful coffee shop, but behind a door in the rear is a secret base for heroes that utilize the most advanced science to battle evil. Well then, lets defend our tranquil planet Earth from the clutches of evil.

name: Park Clubhouse
desc: Whether you prefer to chill out by the fountain, or dance with your friends in the music pavilion, there is always a good reason to come and visit this peaceful art-d co public park. Contains a go-kart racing game, a rythm-action game, and the Space Crash arcade cabinet. Playing the games will get you rewards.

name: Twilight Lounge
desc: The luxurious Twilight Lounge is the hangout of the elite. With designer seating, chic lighting, a funky bar, and even a hot tub this is the place to be seen.

name: Cutthroats Hideaway Apartment
desc: The best spot from which to embark upon your next swashbuckling adventure.. No matter the plunders you seek, you and your friends will have the time of your life. Check out the pirate ship, walk the plank, shadow dancing, play checkers, best your mateys at liars dice, or furnish your space with all your ill-begotten gains. All this and an ocean view. Thee place to assemble before going off to play Cutthroats  Battle for Black Powder Cove.

name: The Dream Yacht  Arctic Voyage
desc: Treat them to the sights of breathtaking glaciers, giant ice formations and crystal blue waters with the Dream Yacht  Arctic Voyage. Explore three decks, chill out on the private ice shelf and collect 20 unique rewards. Live the dream.

name: Luxury Weekend Lake House
desc: Enjoy a bit of rest and relaxation in this modern two-story lake house complete with a kitchen, bedroom, and dock with your very own rowboat. The stunning backdrop for the perfect weekend getaway is set on the edge of a tantalizing lake and mystically docile forestry. In addition to that, the serene life-like atmosphere of dancing fire-flies and migrating birds will surely erase any motivation of returning to the busy city streets.

name: Gothic Cathedral - Clubhouse
desc: This ancient abandoned cathedral on the cliff is a sanctuary and a place you call home. From the majestic room, moonlit courtyard, to the massive candlelit hall, you can be the ruler of the night.

name: SeaClyff Night Clubhouse
desc: A radical nightclub space with all the essentials. Food in the fridge, tunes in the stereo and lots of space for multi-level dance floor action. State of the art everything. The doors are automatic, the appliances are interactive, even the shower and toilet work (an essential at any party). Four floors of fun in a hi-tech heaven that would make even the Great Gatsby jealous. If lavish is your lifestyle, then this is your new party pad.

name: LKWD Life Paradise Marina
desc: An idyllic marina apartment perfect for spending the night before your next big adventure. Luxuriate in stylish surroundings with a stunning tropical sunset view, exotic wildlife and magnificent craft around you.

name: neotopia hub apartment
desc: Take up residence in the neotopia hub apartment. www.neotopia.co

name: Old West Saloon Clubhouse
desc: Take pride as the new owner of The Old West Saloon today. Youve worked hard moving westward to explore the new frontier, and its time to take pride in your latest acquisition. The Saloon is the perfect place to host friends with included games of Blackjack, Liars Dice and even Darts. But no new piece of real estate would be complete without a wardrobe so included is Old West attire and furniture to truly give your new home an authentic look and feel. This Saloon is so jammed packed with items and minigames youll be the talk of the town. The Old West Saloon space is a clubhouse where everyone is invited to join.

name: Gothic Cathedral
desc: This ancient abandoned cathedral on the cliff is a sanctuary and a place you call home. From the majestic room, moonlit courtyard, to the massive candlelit hall, you can be the ruler of the night.

name: SeaClyff Clubhouse
desc: A radical club space with all the essentials. Food in the fridge, tunes in the stereo and lots of space for multi-level dance floor action. State of the art everything. The doors are automatic, the appliances are interactive, even the shower and toilet work (an essential at any party). Four floors of fun in a hi-tech heaven that would make even the Great Gatsby jealous. If lavish is your lifestyle, then this is your new party pad.

name: Oscars Lobster Mania Island
desc: Feed Oscar those lobsters till you drop, or just wander the sandy beach in the midday sun.

name: Batman  Arkham Asylum Batcave Outpost
desc: Batman  Arkham Asylum Batcave Key

name: RaceOn Garage
desc: This garage is not just for cars, its the pinnacle of cool when it comes to a meeting place for people in PlayStation Home. Be one of the edgy first to own this stunning space and decide what you want to use it for. Organize an underground party or convert it into the most modern of living space or keep it as a working space, the choices are endless.

name: Hot Sandy Beach Just For Two
desc: Vacation On A Luxurious Private Beach. The Clear Blue Ocean, The Wide Sandy Beach, And The Cottages On The Sea Are All Yours. With Your Friends, With Your Lover. Your Vacation Has Just Begun.

name: The Greenhouse
desc: Enjoy the wonderful atmosphere and gardens around this Victorian style Greenhouse. This newly restored piece of architecture retains the charm and the beauty of the old days. Surrounded by a lake and luscious green areas, it is the perfect place to hang around alone or with friends.

name: The Secret Party Garden  Clubhouse
desc: Host your own secret party within the secluded walls of this luscious garden. Chill out by the lily pond, or put your feet up on the patio and take in the tranquil surroundings.

name: Aurora Showcase Apartment
desc: The perfect apartment for showcasing your rewards and purchases.

name: RaceOn Garage
desc: This garage is not just for cars, its the pinnacle of cool when it comes to a meeting place for people in PlayStation HOME. Be one of the edgy first to own this stunning space and decide what you want to use it for. Organize an underground party or convert it into the most modern of living space or keep it as a working space, the choices are endless.

name: Emos Garage Loft
desc: Your very own Emo Ray Garage Loft. A great place to relax after saving the world from intergalactic teddy bears. This apartment connects directly into the Public and Game spaces for Emo Ray Vs. Intergalactic Teddy Bears.

name: Mystery Key - (#2 of 3)
desc: This Mystery Key will fast become your favorite. Collect all three.

name: Men in Black Headquarters - Clubhouse
desc: You ll have an all-access pass when you own the Men In Black Headquarters as your own Club House. Hold your meetings in the MIB Offices, shop in the armory and relax in the break room. The MIB HQ is the perfect set-up for your secret, underground organization. So suit up and get ready for the explosive return of Agents Kay and Jay in Men in Black III and the epic new video game Men in Black  Alien Crisis .

name: Gothic Manor
desc: Welcome to the Gothic Manor, where it s always midnight and the moon is constantly hovering in the starry night sky. You ll enjoy the Manors dark Victorian style themes such as the grand ballroom on the first floor, and a second story balcony that overlooks an outside courtyard, complete with its own man-made pond.

name: The House - Clubhouse
desc: The LIVING Collection - The House. Remember... Fashion passes, style remains, LIVING is the key.

name: City of Flowers Penthouse Window to the World
desc: Make this apartment penthouse in downtown Paris yours, between the Eiffel Tower and the Arc de Triomphe. Your life in the city of flowers, Paris, begins here.

name: Valor Barracks
desc: Valor Barracks - For Valor employees, the barracks are your home away from home. This apartment has all the amenities a soldier should ever need. Theres fresh mountain air, tall evergreen trees and a heavily armed chopper just around the corner.

name: PlayStation Home Mansion - Second Floor
desc: Step onto the second-story floor of the PlayStation Home Mansion and experience the frills of a life lived in luxury. Indulge yourself in a classic game of pool or the darts mini-game that comes included in your new game lounge. Couple that with a sleek juice bar, a library fit for a Greek scholar, and a lavishly decorated bedroom and you re living life like a king. As an added bonus, each section of the PlayStation Home Mansion includes up to 5 unique gold rewards for you and your guests.

name: Xi Vertigo Apartment
desc: This Massive And Fantastical Outdoor Apartment, Situated On The Side Of A Skyscraper Overlooking A Futuristic City, Defies Belief.

name: Audi Apartment
desc: The Audi apartment is your reward for reaching the skies in the Audi Vertical Run game. Enjoy the view of the city below or relax while watching selected Audi content.

name: Playground Apartment
desc: This Apartment boasts beautiful views of the Playground, the Buser Bridge, and the Quevedo River. It is furnished with the latest in parquet flooring, lighting fixtures, and radiator heating.

name: The Secret Party Garden  Apartment
desc: Host your own secret party within the secluded walls of this luscious garden. Chill out by the lily pond, or put your feet up on the patio and take in the tranquil surroundings.

name: The Painted Bare Studio
desc: The Painted Bare Studio is the ideal place to let your artistic imagination run wild. So unpack your artist equipment and get settled in. But what will you use this loft apartment for, a workspace, a living space, a gallery or as the perfect backdrop to a social event? The choice is yours with this versatile apartment.

name: Lock-a-doodle Studio (Clubhouse)
desc: The perfect setting for all your doodling. The Lock-a-doodle Studio includes a built in Lock-a-doodle mini-game plus a Gallery to display all your finest Doodles created in-game.

name: The Dressing Room
desc: This environment is undoubtedly the most distinguished and elegant on PlayStation Home. Characterised by its spaciousness, light and class, it has been specially created for those who appreciate quality and good taste. The Dressing Room is not only a masterpiece of architecture, but also a work of art.

name: Ansada Fone Apartment (Night)
desc: This is a special version of the Ansada Fone Apartment that was won from playing the OMG Trap-O-Matic in Aurora. Dont forget to check out the other cool apartments and clubhouses from nDreams.

name: A School Life Full Of Memories
desc: One Floor Of The School Building Is Yours, Including Two Classrooms, The Purchasing Department And The Hallway. The Layout Is Up To You, Including Desks And Chairs. Create Your Own Classroom And Enjoy School Life With Your Friends. However, Dont Stay At School Until Late At Night. You Never Know What Might Happen...

name: Xi Party House
desc: A Nighttime Party Apartment With Pumping Electronic Dance Music. Whats In The Safe And How Do You Open It?

name: Cutteridge Estate
desc: Unlock the mysteries of Cutteridge Estate. This elegant Victorian estate is rumored to be the final resting place of many dark and depraved souls. Do you dare to venture into these forsaken halls in search of the secrets which lie within?

name: Nebula Air Ship
desc: Take to the skies as a nautical air pilot as you maneuver your air ship through the soft billowy clouds. From atop your sky deck you will truly have a bird s eye view of the land down below. You might even catch a glimpse of other air ships flying in the distance. Reward your guests with a Miniature Airship item, exclusive to Nebula Air Ship personal space.

name: The Pearl Diver Apartment
desc: Spend some time beneath the waves in your own submarine, The Pearl Diver. Designed for combing through the sea floor, this underwater vessel is enclosed by glass to allow you to fully enjoy the aquatic sea life. Reward you and your friends with the exclusive Pearl Diver Mini-Fish Tank furniture item, only available in The Pearl Diver Apartment.

name: A Tranquil Personal Garden
desc: Your Own Garden, Received From The Kingdom Of Planta. Create Your Own Beautiful Garden By Planting Plantas And Arranging Furniture.

name: Fossil Museum
desc: In this personal space, the fossils that you found in the Southern Island Hideaway lounge are exhibited.

name: The Jewel of the Skies
desc: The Jewel of the Skies was once a flourishing village in the clouds, each palace and dwelling accessible only by flying carpet. Long ago this magical knowledge was lost and the towers and spires gradually fell into disrepair until only a few remained. Awaken the Genie, unleash his magic and reap the rewards. Flying Carpet Gem Collection Mini-game Interactive Genie Unlockable rewards and apartment customisations

name: PlayStation Home Mansion - Garage
desc: A mansion isn t really a mansion without an expensive place to keep your rides. That s why we created an over-sized four-door garage to accompany the PlayStation Home Mansion. Your showroom comes equipped with overhead lights to help showoff your prized trophies. There is more to this fancy showroom that meets the eye can you find the missing pieces? As an added bonus, each section of the PlayStation Home Mansion includes up to 5 unique gold rewards for you and your guests.

name: Island Bungalow Apartment
desc: Nestled on the edge of a tropical paradise, this exquisite Island Bungalow is hidden somewhere on an uncharted coastline. Be the first to explore this mysterious paradise.

name: The Campsite
desc: Hitch up your horse, and put some beans on the fire. This is your very own campsite. It may not be much, but at least youve got something to protect you from the elements.

name: Acorn Meadows Park Apartment - Autumn
desc: Your own little private slice of Acorn Meadows Park, this lakeside garden apartment provides the perfect place to relax and take time away from the main Park without leaving the Acorn Meadows environment.

name: Winter Vacation Villa
desc: Experience the frills and chills of this ski chalet winter wonderland overlooked by an icy cascading waterfall and nestled neatly in between a snowy cliff and snow-dressed forest. Complete with its own outdoor jacuzzi, indoor fireplace, and veranda bedroom, this is how the winter holiday was meant to be spent.

name: SeaClyff Night Retreat
desc: A night version of one of the most alive spaces you will ever spend time in. It has all the best parts of the day space and dynamic outdoor lighting that can be turned on and off. Even the hot tub has its own lighting. There are a few enhancements including all new music. A must have for people who like the best of everything.

name: Prehistoric Canyon
desc: Enjoy panoramic views of dramatic waterfalls and lush grassland from your bamboo hut perched high above Prehistoric Canyon. Dinosaurs and prehistoric mammals roam the surroundings, from peaceful Mammoth families to ferocious T-Rex. Play the Dinosaur Spotting mini game to record the prehistoric creatures that visit every day and earn rewards guests can play too.

name: Underwater Apartment
desc: Its wet out there.

name: Tuscan Villa Clubhouse
desc: Enjoy a day in the countryside at your elaborate Tuscan Villa. This two-room lodging has a swanky living room connected to an outdoor porch and patio. To make things better, we ve added an indoor swimming pool in the very next room. This is the perfect place to lay out and get to know your guests better. The Tuscan Villa space is a clubhouse where everyone is invited to join.

name: Frozen Peak Palace
desc: Surround yourself in the frosty splendors of the Frozen Peak Palace. Made entirely from blocks of ice, this frosty getaway comes with a rare piece of art and an inglenook with a glacial blue flame. Reward your guests with a Frozen Peak Palace Throne item, exclusive to Frozen Peak Palace personal space.

name: Relaxing Edo Bathhouse
desc: A relaxing atmosphere for body and soul. Invite a friend, take a soak together in the soothing waters, and watch the days fatigue melt away.

name: Summer with sunflowers blooming
desc: A personal space where you can enjoy the good old Japanese summer.

name: The Casino  Penthouse Suite
desc: Welcome to our exclusive Penthouse suite strictly reserved for those in our Millionaires Club. The concierge is on standby 24 hours a day to manage any of your needs. Enjoy your stay at the Paradise Hotel and Casino.

name: The Hangar Skatepark
desc: This skatepark is housed within a huge repurposed aircraft Hangar. Its open, its spacious, its everything an avid skater ever dreamed of. With ramps, bowls, grind rails and half pipes, its time to get on your deck and skate around this large skatepark.

name: The Midnight Glade
desc: A Secluded Glade Under A Moonlit Starry Sky. Gather Around The Solitary Tree And Warm Yourself By The Glow Of The Fire. Its The Perfect Place For A Fireworks Party.

name: Ratchet and Clank  Home Sweet Home
desc: Enjoy the space view from your Ratchet and Clank apartment.

name: The Casino  Budget Room
desc: We hope you enjoyed playing at The Casino. As a first time player weve managed to find a spare room in section B3 in our former hotel space. Were happy to offer one of our VIP Suites as soon as youve shown the true card shark you are. Good Luck.

name: Warhawk Apartment
