desc: Your personal flying fortress will keep you safe while you and your friends plan your next attack with the Warhawk Sand Table. Jump back into the fight with a friend in the co-operative 2-player Warhawk Turret Shooter, competing for the high score on your personal leaderboard.

name: City by the Bay Loft Window to the World
desc: A large loft in central San Francisco along the cable car line. You can live there or open up a shop. Its up to you. Starting today, you too are a member of the City by the Bay.

name: Xi Party House
desc: Your very own slice of Xi - the perfect nighttime party palace.

name: Aurora Island
desc: Your very own slice of Aurora - It is a place to relax and contemplate. Well, when Aurora isnt under attack.

name: Luxurious tropical paradise beach crib
desc: Some would call it Heaven, some a palace, in Europe they call it a villa, some Americans a mansion, but most just call it a hut. This modern 21st century building in the sticks and straw style has an advanced virtual room system that is impossible to find. It has a large private area with a domed games room. Although it has a classic flavour, the home has a few unique qualities. It s also an amazing place for parties.

name: The Boutique Apartment
desc: This FREE apartment from nDreams is the perfect place for the suave and sexy socialites of PlayStation Home. Show off your social status by purchasing the additional rooms. Unlock all of the rooms for a collection of prestigious reward items.

name: Masquerade Ball - The Ballroom Club House (Gothic)
desc: The perfect Club House to host a lavish Gothic themed Masquerade Ball. Entertain your guests in this beautiful ballroom. Deck out your ballroom with the Gothic Masquerade Ball furniture range for extra authenticity. Please note, in order to access this Club House you will need to have purchased the Club House slot from either the Estates Store or the Clubs menu (available in Options).

name: Low Tide Lounge
desc: Low Tide Lounge

name: Tree House Personal Apartment
desc: A stunning circular treehouse built around the trunk of an ancient tree high up in the mountains. Made of wood and circular in design, there are two levels each offering spectacular views of the waterfalls and mountains outside.

name: The Imperial Voyager
desc: Traverse the great blue yonder in Professor Sidwell s patented steampunk skyship, the legendary Imperial Voyager.

name: The Country Chic - Tour Bus - Clubhouse
desc: The time has come to hit the road and party. Take full advantage of the freedoms a virtual world provides, slip the bus into cruise control and join the party at full speed. Just remember what goes on tour, stays on tour.

name: Hillside Clubhouse
desc: Built with a view in mind, the Hillside Clubhouse is the place to get away from the confines of a concrete jungle and bask in the luxury of a home away from home. The Hillside House space is a clubhouse where everyone is invited to join.

name: Rainy Day Apartment
desc: When the sun is setting and its wet outside, there really is no place like home...

name: Penthouse in La Ville-Lumi re From The Window of the World
desc: A penthouse which is located close to Paris urban area, Eiffel tower and Triumphal arch is yours. The life in Paris, La Ville-Lumi re, starts now.

name: Gnome Curling Secret Garden
desc: Enjoy Gnome Curling in the privacy of your own secret garden. Comes complete with a gazebo, beautiful floral displays and a magical door to take you back home again. When you purchase this apartment you also receive  Gnome Curling - Standard Gnome Gnome Curling - Fat Gnome Gnome Curling - Skinny Gnome Gnome Curling - Bouncy Gnome Gnome Curling - Explosive Gnome Gnome Curling - Ninja Gnome Gnome Curling - Stinky Gnome Gnome Curling - Sexy Gnome

name: Dolphy Room
desc: A relaxing virtual space where you can raise and interact with your own Dolphy.

name: Moon Forest Clubhouse
desc: Camping will never be the same after you spend a night at the Moon Forest Clubhouse. Complete with an outdoor fire pit, this three room exotic getaway is a great way to lose yourself in nature and spend time with friends. The Moon Forest Clubhouse is a space where everyone is invited to join.

name: City by the Bay Loft Window to the World
desc: A large loft in central San Francisco along the cable car line. You can live there or open up a shop. Its up to you. Starting today, you too are a member of the City by the Bay.

name: Plum Tree Pavilion Clubhouse
desc: Take a deep breath and inhale the soft sweet aroma of the Plum Tree Pavilion. Its gentle landscaping and exquisite architecture makes this space ideal for anyone who s a fan of fishponds and rock formations, to own. The Plum Tree Pavilion is a clubhouse where everyone is invited to join.

name: Palace of the Seven Winds Clubhouse
desc: Reign over your own celestial paradise with the Palace of the Seven Winds. Exert your influence over the heavens themselves to alter time, break free of your earthly shackles and take to the skies, lounge in your own personal harem-style apartments, have wishes granted by your personal genie, unlock rewards and much more.

name: Diamond Beach Mansion
desc: Enter the most luxurious personal space in PlayStation Home. The Diamond Beach Mansion is packed with special features befitting the rich and famous from a gifting machine that lets you give your friends exclusive virtual items (and rewards just for the owner), to fully-functional appliances and fun interactives like the user-controlled weather and day night cycles. The Diamond Beach Mansion includes four extensions  1st Floor, 2nd Floor, backyard, and private yacht that you can buy in any order. Collect all four areas of the Diamond Beach Mansion to unlock a secret area.

name: Masquerade Ball - The Ballroom (Gothic)
desc: The perfect personal space to host a lavish Gothic themed Masquerade Ball. Entertain your guests in this beautiful ballroom. Deck out your ballroom with the Gothic Masquerade Ball furniture range for extra authenticity.

name: Nostalgic University Days
desc: Make the first floor of a university building yours, including two classrooms, a shop, and a hallway. The layout of desks, chairs, and other items is up to you. Make your own unique classroom and enjoy university life along with your friends. Be careful not to stay at university until late at night. You never know what might happen...

name: Paradise Health Club  Clubhouse
desc: Relax and re-energise in the exotic and picturesque grounds of Paradise Health Club. Chill out by the pool, sunbathe on the terrace or detox in the sauna.

name: F.U.B.A.R. Apartment (+DOUBLE POINTS)
desc: This unique outdoor apartment contains a scaled copy of your own amazing military base from the FREE game F.U.B.A.R. (Fight Until Blood And Ruin) and earns you DOUBLE POINTS in key sections of the game, helping you rank up much faster. Observe your master piece of war from the comfort of your own home and show it off to your friends.

name: Moon Forest Apartment
desc: Camping will never be the same after you spend a night at the Moon Forest Apartment. Complete with an outdoor fire pit, this three room exotic getaway is a great way to lose yourself in nature and spend time with friends. Reward yourself and your friends with exclusive camping gear furniture item, only available in the Moon Forest Apartment.

name: Acorn Meadows Park Apartment
desc: Your own little private slice of Acorn Meadows Park, this lakeside garden apartment provides the perfect place to relax and take time away from the main Park without leaving the Acorn Meadows environment.

name: City Penthouse
desc: A luxury apartment in the heart of the city designed around a split level layout. Additional highlights include exquisite water features, unique lighting solutions and an incredible view of the city skyline.

name: The Complex
desc: This FREE apartment is brought to you by nDreams. Expand your complex by getting any or all of the additional rooms. On doing so, you wont only impress your friends with a great apartment but you will be rewarded for your efforts.

name: Hollywood Hills House Daytime Clubhouse (with Home Theater)
desc: Entertain and meet with your club in this ultra-exclusive clubhouse, set in the Hollywood Hills above the LA skyline. Features include  Built-in Entertainment On Demand theater system A swimming feature for the infinity pool. THIS is the ultra-exclusive retreat for the discerning club owner. Purchase of this clubhouse comes bundled with the LOOT Active Camera and Active Light, so you can film your parties and upload them to YouTube. PLEASE READ  Due to contractual and rights agreements, all content may not be available in all countries. Content availability is dependent on the geolocation of the device. CRACKLE content is only available in US, CA, UK, and AU. RADIOIO is only available in US and CA. Only one LOOT TV or LOOT Radio can be active at a time.

name: Sodium Blimp
desc: Step aboard your very own dirigible. Sodium pilots all need a way to travel from one track to another and many prefer to go via Blimp. If you get adventurous while on your travels, why not stop for a digging session, who knows what treasures the desert floor might yield. Includes  Flying minigame Digging minigame with 13 exclusive PlayStation Home rewards and the chance to earn Sodium resources The ability to complete new public and secret VICKIE challenges in return for Sodium Credits

name: Waterfall Terrace
desc: Waterfall Terrace is the perfect secluded get away - Fish and enjoy nature in all its splendor.

name: Underwater Apartment
desc: Its wet out there

name: LKWD Life Lakeside Oasis
desc: Enjoy the subtle elegance and modern asthetic of this beautiful personal space. A just reward for your hard efforts in LKWD Life.

name: Tuscan Villa Apartment
desc: Enjoy a day in the countryside at your elaborate Tuscan Villa. This two-room lodging has a swanky living room connected to an outdoor porch and patio. To make things better, we ve added an indoor swimming pool in the very next room. This is the perfect place to lay out and get to know your guests better. Reward yourself and your friends with an exclusive Tuscan Villa Pizza furniture item, only available in the Tuscan Villa Apartment.

name: Ansada Fone Apartment
desc: This truly unique apartment isnt like anything you have ever seen before in PlayStation Home. A fantastic cartoon world where you can play a frantic 4 player mini game with your friends or chill out and redecorate. Will you get there in time to Ansada Fone?

name: Edo Row Houses
desc: This personal space re-creates the collective residences on the back streets in the humantiy-overflowing Edo period. If you own this personal space, you can use Operation  Defend Edo Row Houses as a recovery spot.

name: Infinite Oasis Ranch Apartment
desc: The perfect place for a mid-summer retreat, the Infinite Oasis Ranch has it all. From lively cacti and ageless palm trees to panoramic views of the surrounding mountain ridge, this space packs it all. Reward yourself and your friends with the exclusive Infinite Oasis Ranch Hay Chair, only available in the Infinite Oasis Ranch Apartment.

name: Plum Tree Pavilion Apartment
desc: Take a deep breath and inhale the soft sweet aroma of the Plum Tree Pavilion. Its gentle landscaping and exquisite architecture makes this space ideal for anyone who s a fan of fishponds and rock formations, to own. Reward you and your friends with an exclusive Lantern furniture item, only available in the Plum Tree Pavilion Apartment.

name: MiniBots Training Facility
desc: This personal space allows you to design and control a custom MiniBot in a fast-paced multiplayer third person shooter for 2-8 players. Battle it out in a last-bot standing Free-for-all brawl or group with friends for Team Arena mode. Complete hidden achievements to unlock unique rewards.

name: Uncharted Fortune Hunters Apartment
desc: Being a fortune hunter is never easy. It means having to travel to the ends of the Earth and rarely staying in one place too long. Good thing you have an apartment like this to call home.

name: Stately Home Clubhouse
desc: The Stately Home is the perfect Clubhouse for those people who like the finer things in life. With its large and beautiful grounds and a direct link through to the Masquerade Ball - The Ballroom Clubhouse, this space is a must-have. Also comes with five free rewards.

name: Pink Paradise - Tour Bus
desc: The time has come to hit the road and party. Take full advantage of the freedoms a virtual world provides, slip the bus into cruise control and join the party at full speed. Just remember what goes on tour, stays on tour.

name: The Nightclub  Apartment
desc: The Nightclub is the perfect venue for a fantastic night out. Dance to pumping music tracks on the dance floor, sip on drinks in the lounge area, or activate the foam cannon for an extra crazy night.

name: Studio Stage Set from LOOT
desc: The Modular Stage Set takes professional machinima to the next level. It provides the user with unprecedented levels of control over the floor, walls, backdrops, lights and camera systems. Also included are the Portable Camera and Portable Light active items, which let you take the LOOT machinima tools to any private space you own, transforming it into a perfect location for shooting your movies and TV shows. It is the ultimate tool for having fun with your friends while bringing new stories to life.

name: Luxury Racing Box
desc: On your mark. Get set. . . GO. If youre a racing fan, make a pit stop here in this exclusive personal space.

name: Glittering Sands Secluded Retreat
desc: Spend your holiday on a luxurious private beach. The clear blue sea, the white sandy beach, and the cottage on the ocean are all yours. With a friend, or with that special someone. Your holiday has just begun.

name: SeaClyff Retreat
desc: Floor-to-ceiling windows in most rooms looking out on an unobstructed view of the ocean. The four floors include a large master bedroom which opens up to a balcony and a study with your choice of wallpaper. An open floor plan with lots of natural light. A large living room, dining room with fireplace and finished basement. Kitchen recently upgraded with high end working appliances. A built in hot tub and expansive deck areas with stunning views. All doors are automatic. Included is a built in sound system, games, plus rewards for the owner and guests. It truly has more features than can be listed here. It is a must see to believe.

name: Oscars Lobster Mania Island
desc: Feed Oscar those lobsters till you drop, or just wander the sandy beach in the midday sun.

name: Club Luminosity
desc: This is the ultimate place to share your love of neon. If you love things that glow, then this place is for you.

name: SuperStar - Jetsetter Private Plane
desc: Take a ride in the ultra luxurious private plane. This flying home has everything a superstar needs, including the best pilots around. Show off like a super star.

name: Old West Saloon
desc: Take pride as the new owner of The Old West Saloon today. Youve worked hard moving westward to explore the new frontier, and its time to take pride in your latest acquisition. The Saloon is the perfect place to host friends with included games of Blackjack, Liars Dice and even Darts. But no new piece of real estate would be complete without a wardrobe so included is Old West attire and furniture to truly give your new home an authentic look and feel. This Saloon is so jammed packed with items and minigames youll be the talk of the town.

name: Def Jam Rapstar Studio
desc: State of the art in-home recording and mixing studio.

name: PC Primitive Dwelling
desc: An Unusual Personal Space Built In The Primitive World Where PC Primitives Are Set. Light The Rooms With primitive Lamps And Enhance The Dwellings With primitive Furniture That Can Be Obtained From Time To Time At Rivers And Other Places. The Primitive Furniture Is An Exclusive Item For This Personal Space.

name: Drop Science Subway
desc: This derelict station was deserted long ago and is now the coolest party space, hidden from the city. Turn the music up, dance, and socialise into the late hours.

name: Masquerade Ball - The Ballroom Club House
desc: The perfect Club House to host a lavish Masquerade Ball. Entertain your guests in this beautiful ballroom. Deck out your ballroom with the Masquerade Ball furniture range for extra authenticity. Please note, in order to access this Club House you will need to have purchased the Club House slot from either the Estates Store or the Clubs menu (available in Options).

name: Mahjong apartment
desc: Looking for a nice and tranquil place to stay? The Mahjong apartment is just the place. This walled apartment in an busy Orient city is an oasis of rest with blossom trees and koi carps. If you are looking for something more lively you can try the Mahjong Attack game that comes with the apartment. Mahjong Attack is a challenging variant of Mahjong Solitaire which is all about speed. You play the game alone (single player), together with your friends (co-op) or against your friends (multiplayer).

name: Tearoom, Golden Monastery
desc: The luxurious and gorgeous golden tearoom. Among the trees one can see its sparkling golden form, said to take your breath away. In this mountain region far removed from civilization, you can spend some time with a cup of tea, cut off from everyday life. * A gift from GZ gift

name: The Dream Yacht  Arctic Voyage Clubhouse
desc: Treat yourself to the sights of breathtaking glaciers, giant ice formations and crystal blue waters with the Dream Yacht  Arctic Voyage. Explore three decks, chill out on the private ice shelf and collect 8 unique rewards. Live the dream.

name: The Bunker Bar
desc: The Bunker Bar is the ultimate live music venue. A dynamically lit stage dominates one side of the space with an ultra cool, chic bar and hangout to the other side. Party.

name: Planetland
desc: This is the personal space for the more adventurous Home buyer. Space is limited, so act now.

name: Castle Durrant
desc: An understated residence for aspiring nobility to call their own. A perfect place to relax and hold out against the siege of life.

name: Doctor Who TARDIS - Clubhouse
desc: TARDIS stands for Time And Relative Dimension In Space. The TARDIS looks like a 1950 s wooden Police Phone Box on the outside, but is of infinite proportions on the inside. Amaze your friends when they discover the wonder of Time Lord technology. Doctor Who logo 2013 and TM BBC. Licensed by BBC WW Ltd.

name: Neptune Suite
desc: The Neptune Suite offers a virtual life of luxury in this opulent underwater paradise. Enjoy this action-packed personal space featuring an 8-player picture scramble game, a 4-player action game, an interactive robotic pet, and a sweeping underwater glass wall vista. Buy now.

name: Paradise Health Club  Apartment
desc: Relax and re-energise in the exotic and picturesque grounds of Paradise Health Club. Chill out by the pool, sunbathe on the terrace or detox in the sauna.

name: Mahjong Apartment
desc: Looking For A Nice And Tranquil Place To Stay? The Mahjong Apartment Is Just The Place. This Walled Apartment In An Busy Orient City Is An Oasis Of Rest With Blossom Trees And Koi Carps. If You Are Looking For Something More Lively You Can Try The Mahjong Attack Game That Comes With The Apartment. Mahjong Attack Is A Challenging Variant Of Mahjong Solitaire Which Is All About Speed. You Play The Game Alone (single Player), Together With Your Friends (co-op) Or Against Your Friends (multiplayer).

name: Tropical Escape
desc: Warm, humid, and exotic. For a small fee, you too can own a piece of Paradise.

name: Basic Clubhouse
desc: The Basic Clubhouse for you to customise as you wish.

name: My Secret Villa on a Blue Whale
desc: Take a trip through the ocean on the back of a whale. Visit tropical countries, the Mediterranean, and even the northern fjords. It s up to you where you steer the gentle giant as you enjoy this relaxing cruise.

name: The House - Apartment
desc: The LIVING Collection - The House. Remember... Fashion passes, style remains, LIVING is the key.

name: Stately Home (Gothic)
desc: The Stately Home (Gothic) is the perfect personal apartment space for those people who like the finer things in life with a slightly darker twist. With its large and beautiful grounds and a direct link through to the Masquerade Ball - The Ballroom (Gothic), this space is a must-have. Also comes with five free rewards.

name: VEEMEEs 50s Diner
desc: Dont be a square on those summer nights and head down to the VEEMEE 50s Diner to hand jive, grab some food and hang with friends.

name: SFRGBT.. Tropical Island
desc: Enjoy a penalty shoot-out against the worlds greatest robot goalkeeper on your very own tropical island at dusk. In addition to the SFRGBT.. minigame, the island comes complete with beach shelter, roaring fire and a boat to take you home again. The minigame also includes 4 unique reward items (sand castle, bucket and spade, SFRGBT.. face ball and shark fin wearable accessory) which can only be won by playing against robo-goalie in this exclusive Personal Space.

name: Cutteridge Estate
desc: Unlock the mysteries of Cutteridge Mansion. This elegant Victorian mansion is rumored to be the final resting place of many dark and depraved souls. Do you dare to venture into these forsaken halls in search of the secrets which lie within?

name: Edo Row Houses
desc: This personal space re-creates the collective residences on the back streets in the humantiy-overflowing Edo period. If you own this personal space, you can use

name: Avalon Keep
desc: The Avalon Keep is an impregnable fortress on your very own floating island. The magical crystals of Avalon allow the landmass to stay afloat and power all the new technological advances that have swept the world of Avalon. Your Keep sets you apart as one of the nobility that have taken residence in the skies around Avalon. Master all the mini-games and share the wealth with the latest in gift machine technology. Can you unlock all the secrets of your Keep?

name: Stately Home
desc: The Stately Home is the perfect personal apartment space for those people who like the finer things in life. With its large and beautiful grounds and a direct link through to the Masquerade Ball - The Ballroom, this space is a must-have. Also comes with five free rewards.

name: S.V.E.R. Barracks
desc: S.V.E.R. Barracks - The S.V.E.R. barracks is your private getaway to remote Central Asia. It features a spectacular sunset view, so you can relax on your large balcony, clean your rifle and watch strike fighters fly through the sun kissed heavens.

name: Lock-a-doodle Studio
desc: The perfect setting for all your doodling. The Lock-a-doodle Studio includes a built in Lock-a-doodle mini-game plus a Gallery to display all your finest Doodles created in-game.

name: Tron Apartment
desc: Experience life on the grid in this apartment from Tron Evolution.

name: LocoIsland
desc: This Is A Personal Space Where You Can Have The South Island Of LocoRoco Characters All To Yourself. This Island Is Full Of Playfulness. You Can Add Facilities By Collecting Nuts From The Island And Communicating With The Inhabitants. There Are Swings, A Slide, A Jukebox, And Even A Game That Can Be Played By Two People. The More You Play, The More Lively And Fun Loco Island Will Become. Enjoy The Personal Space With A Lot Of Volume.

name: Hollyridge Estate Clubhouse
desc: The Hollyridge Estate is the perfect setting for an elegant winter soiree. This personal space features classic Victorian architecture and design and also features built-in decorating options which allow you to create a festive atmosphere without taking up any furniture slots. Includes customizable wallpaper, a snowball fight minigame and much more.

name: Martial Art Place
desc: Personal Space Of The Exercise Hall Type Which Trains A Martial Art. Seemingly, The Decoyed Game Is Lived And Attached.

name: Cosmic Corner - Fun Sized Apartment
desc: An affordable apartment from nDreams. For some reason a piece of this planet has broken away and is now floating between the Earth and the Moon. With stunning views of both it could be a perfect getaway to chill out amongst the stars.

name: Musicality Apartment
desc: A unique live music venue - up to four players can grab an instrument and jam compete against each other. Comes complete with the Dance music pack additional packs are available to purchase at the Musicality shop.

name: Hidden Oak Retreat
desc: Welcome to the Hidden Oak Retreat, a clubhouse retreat tucked away in the mountains. Get away from the hustle of city life and enjoy one of the two relaxing fireplaces. Look up and and youll notice the clubhouse lit by chandeliers made of antlers. Head out to the deck and enjoy the lakefront view while you roast some marshmallows on the campfire. Now this is the great outdoors. The Hidden Oak Retreat space is a clubhouse where everyone is invited to join.

name: SFRGBT.. Tropical Island
desc: Enjoy a penalty shoot-out against the worlds greatest robot goalkeeper on your very own tropical island at dusk. In addition to the SFRGBT.. minigame, the island comes complete with beach shelter, roaring fire and a boat to take you home again. The minigame also includes 4 unique reward items (sand castle, bucket and spade, Mr. Wilson face ball and shark fin wearable accessory) which can only be won by playing against robo-goalie in this exclusive Personal Space.

name: The Space Station
desc: The Space Station needs a crew, and youve been selected to take part in an all new out-of-this-world experience. Your Space Station adventure will have you defending your new home against incoming asteroids in the fully interactive Station Defense turret center. On top of defending the station your tasks will also include lowering and raising the external shutters so you dont get blinded by the sun and youll even have to evacuate the garbage you produce in to the vaccum of space. Also included with the Space Station is a chair, sofa, custom space helmet and a zero gravity UFO companion object to follow you all around PlayStation Home. Your shuttle is cleared for launch, awaiting your clearance.

name: LocoIsland
desc: This personal space is your very own tropical island inhabited by LocoRoco characters. The tropical retreat is full of exciting activities. Collect nuts that fall from the trees, and communicate with islanders to expand the facilities. Enjoy the Swing, Slide, Jukebox, and games for two players. And the more time you spend on LocoIsland, the more vibrant and exciting the paradise becomes. Treat yourself to this fun-filled personal space.

name: Pirate Galleon Apartment
desc: Moored by a tropical island, this ship comes complete with playable cannon mini-game and four Pirate themed furniture rewards. A very desirable residence that has suddenly become available, due to the imprisonment of the previous owner.

name: The Drey VIP Room (For Female)
desc: You have been cordially invited to be a member of the Drey VIP Room. Take an exclusive look into the inspired fashions of Dreys celebrated designers. The Drey VIP Room features a stunning collection of old and new - everything to satisfy the hunger of the fashion elite worldwide. This includes 22 existing Gift Machine clothing items and 12 exclusive new clothing items.

name: The Pearl Diver Clubhouse
desc: Spend some time beneath the waves in your own submarine, The Pearl Diver. Designed for combing through the sea floor, this underwater vessel is enclosed by glass to allow you to fully enjoy the aquatic sea life. The Pearl Diver space is a clubhouse where everyone is invited to join.

name: Studio Stage Set from LOOT
desc: The Modular Stage Set takes professional machinima to the next level. It provides the user with unprecedented levels of control over the floor, walls, backdrops, lights and camera systems. Also included are the Portable Camera and Portable Light active items, which let you take the LOOT machinima tools to any private space you own, transforming it into a perfect location for shooting your movies and TV shows. It is the ultimate tool for having fun with your friends while bringing new stories to life.

name: Castle Greywold  Clubhouse
desc: In this new clubhouse, you can take up arms in the training yard, entertain guests in the audience chamber, or survey your surroundings from the castle ramparts.

name: Japanese School Days
desc: Make the first floor of a school building yours, including two classrooms, a shop, and a hallway. The layout of desks, chairs, and other items is up to you. Make your own unique classroom and enjoy school life along with your friends. Be careful not to stay at school until late at night. You never know what might happen...

name: Ghost Pirate Ship
desc: LeChucks Pirate ship. Sail the seven seas and even more with the new underground Lava transport hull. Strike fear in the hearts of Sailors and wannabe pirates. The sails may look ripped but they are still fully functional. Avast. And good luck.

name: Polar Rush Tundra Lodge
desc: Jump on your snowmobile and explore the tundra in this exciting new personal space from Lockwood. From your modern apartment, youll be able to look out onto the beautiful arctic surroundings before riding out to see what you can find. Includes Snowmobile Exploration minigame which allows you to cruise around the landscape, perform stunts and find 9 exclusive PlayStation Home rewards.

name: Yacht  Santorini
desc: Docked at Greeks famous Santorini harbor, your yacht is equipped with all the modern virtual conveniences you would expect. Step out on deck to take in the spectacular view or stay inside and relax with some friends.

name: The Lost Dam Hideout
desc: Miles from civilization and hidden deep in a gorge, this long-lost Dam is the perfect hideout for every aspiring evil overlord. The dark interior and bare rock set the mood and the Piranha pool adds a suitable finishing touch.

name: Park personal space
desc: Whether you prefer to chill out by the fountain, or dance with your friends in the music pavilion, there is always a good reason to come and visit this peaceful art-d co public park. Contains a go-kart racing game, a rythm-action game, and the Space Crash arcade cabinet. Playing the games will get you rewards.

name: Prehistoric Valley
desc: Prehistoric Valley is your regular lush mountaintop peaceful idyll it just happens to be around 100 million years ago and inhabited by cave people, dinosaurs, and giant mammals.

name: Tearoom, Aqua Monastery
desc: The luxurious and gorgeous aqua tearoom.Among the trees one can see a sparkling aqua figure, said to take your breath away. In this mountain region far removed from civilization, you can spend some time with a cup of tea, cut off from everyday life. * A present from GZ Gift

name: No Mans Land, Museum Expansion Map.
desc: This map pack allows you to fight on the No Mans Land Museum Map.

name: Blueprint  Home - Cruise Ship Environment
desc: Build your home on the deck of a gigantic cruise ship. Note - You will need to own Blueprint  Home to access this content once it has been purchased.

name: Diamond Beach Infinity Pool
desc: Add a private pool and strech of beach to your Modern Beach Mansion complete with rockwaterfall and cabanas. Go swimming in the pool with custom swim animations, lounge in the sun or wade into the ocean and enjoy the scenery. Did we mention the awesome rock waterfall?. Bring your friends over to swim and gift them with exclusive freebies  Golden Bikini, Golden Swim Trunks, Golden Beach Blanket, Golden Umbrella and Golden Ice Chest.

name: Lock-a-doodle Doodle Pack - Jewel of the Skies
desc: Each Doodle Pack contains new colors, stickers, words and shapes. Please note  Doodle Packs can only be used in conjunction with the Lock-a-doodle mini-game or Active Object, or Lock-a-doodle Gift Edition.

name: Blueprint  Home - Classroom Office Style Pack
desc: This fantastic pack has everything you need to create your perfect classroom office. Purchasing this style pack will unlock the following items for use in your Blueprint  Home. * 7 x Classroom Office Wall Textures * 7 x Classroom Office Corner Pieces * 7 x Classroom Office Windows * 3 x Classroom Office Floor Textures * 3 x Classroom Office Ceiling Textures * 2 x Classroom Office Wall Styles * 1 x Classroom Office Pillar * 1 x Outer Classroom Office Wall * 1 x Outer Classroom Office Window * 1 x Outer Classroom Office Pillar * 1 x Outer Classroom Office Corner * Feature - Classroom Office Desk * Feature - Classroom Office Computer * Feature - Classroom Office Whiteboard All of the above items will become available in Blueprint  Home once this pack has been purchased. You will need to own Blueprint  Home to access these items.

name: Blueprint  Home - Nightclub Style Pack
desc: Have you ever wanted to create your own nightclub? Well now you can with this amazing Blueprint  Home style pack. This pack comes with the following items  * 2 x Nightclub Wall Styles with 5 x Textures Each * 3 x Nightclub Floor Textures * 3 x Nightclub Ceiling Textures * 3 x Nightclub Pillars * 1 x Nightclub Outer Style * Feature - Nightclub Lights * Feature - Nightclub Atmosphere All of the above items will become available in Blueprint  Home once this pack has been purchased. You will need to own Blueprint  Home to access these items.

desc: Purchasing this item will unlock the Silo area within The Complex Apartment.

desc: Each Doodle Pack contains new colors, stickers, words and shapes. Please note  Doodle Packs can only be used in conjunction with the Lock-a-doodle mini-game or Active Object, or Lock-a-doodle Gift Edition.

desc: Purchasing this item will unlock the Bio Dome area within The Complex Apartment.

desc: Purchasing this item will unlock the Garden area within The Complex 2.

desc: EmoRay  Mission Pack 2 gives you an extra mission with story to explore. Purchasing this Mission Pack for Volume One will give you the ability to earn these rewards  -Cuddly Bear Companion -Cuddly Bear Rug (Flooring) Purchasing this Mission Pack adds to your total Volume One leaderboard score. Purchasing and completing all the Mission Packs for Volume One will earn you an extra song for the EmoRay Boombox. *This Mission Pack can only be purchased if you have purchased EmoRay  Volume One.

name: Blueprint  Home - City of the Future Environment
desc: Welcome to the city of the future. What better way to show off your Blueprint  Home. Note - You must own Blueprint  Home by nDreams to use this item.

name: The Complex  Dock
desc: Purchasing this item will unlock the Dock area within The Complex Apartment.

name: The Boutique Apartment  Bathroom
desc: Purchasing this item will unlock the Bathroom area within The Boutique Apartment.

name: Avalon Keep  Dungeon
desc: Explore the hidden depths of your Keep. This expansion also adds to the rewards in the Crystal Hunter game, as well as owner only rewards by feeding the dungeon monster. *The Dungeon can only be purchased if you already own Avalon Keep.

name: The Complex  Officers Lounge
desc: Purchasing this item will unlock the Officers Lounge area within The Complex Apartment.

name: Blueprint  Home - City Penthouse Environment
desc: Build your home atop a huge skyscraper in the middle of a thriving city. Your luxury penthouse will benefit from the best view money can buy. Note - You will need to own Blueprint  Home to access this content once it has been purchased.

name: Blueprint  Home - Wallpaper Pack
desc: This wallpaper pack contains a range of beautifully designed wallpapers. Purchasing this pack will unlock the following items for use in your Blueprint  Home. * 15 x Wall Textures * 15 x Corner Pieces * 15 x Windows * 1 x Pillar * 3 x Floor Textures * 3 x Ceiling Textures * 1 x Wall Styles * 1 x Outer Wall * 1 x Outer Window * 1 x Outer Pillar * 1 x Outer Corner All of the above items will become available in Blueprint  Home once this pack has been purchased. desc: An epic update to Bramblenook Farm. Allows you to select new styles for your Bramblenook Farmhouse, craft new items for yourself and your friends and raise cows. Also contains  Cow Statue, Cow Companion and Calf Companion.

desc: Each Doodle Pack contains new colors, stickers, words and shapes. Please note  Doodle Packs can only be used in conjunction with the Lock-a-doodle mini-game or Active Object, or Lock-a-doodle Gift Edition.

You will need to own Blueprint  Home to access these items.

name: Cutteridge Ghost Stories Bundle
desc: Delve deeper into the mysteries of Cutteridge Estate by purchasing the Cutteridge Ghost Stories bundle. This eerie expansion to Cutteridge Estate reveals the story behind the tormented souls that haunt the Estate and introduces terrifying new minigames with spooky rewards. Bundle includes  4 new minigames and rewards added to the Cutteridge Estate personal space Ghostly Skull Companion Mysterious Lantern (male and female) Evil Pumpkin Complete all four minigames to unlock the ultimate reward. Not for the faint of heart.

name: Diamond Beach Private Yacht
desc: No Beach Mansion is complete without a custom built yacht just for you to entertain guests. The yacht is fully driveable  Just set out for a destination, drop anchor and enjoy the ocean views with your friends on the deck or inside with a full kitchen and living area complete with bar, window shades, sink and bathroom. Share the wealth by gifting friends exclusive freebies  Golden Lounge Chair, Yachting Hat (male and female), Lifebuoy Wall Hanging, and Golden Ship in a Bottle.

name: The Complex 2  Bedroom
desc: Purchasing this item will unlock the Bedroom area within The Complex 2.

desc: Purchasing this item will unlock the Kitchen area within The Boutique Apartment.

desc: A truly sinister style pack that lets you show your darker side. You will need to own Blueprint  Home to access these items.

desc: A beautiful sky that can be used to change the mood in your Blueprint  Home. You will need to own Blueprint  Home to access these items.

You will need to own Blueprint  Home to access these items.

name: Novus Prime Private Hangar
desc: This is a fully functional hangar for your Novus Prime Officers Quarters. With this hangar you can play missions with friends, use the workshop, and collect salaries.

desc: EmoRay  Mission Pack 1 gives you an extra mission with story to explore. Purchasing this Mission Pack for Volume One will give you the ability to earn these rewards  -Hammy Companion -Cuddly Bear Chair (Chair) Purchasing this Mission Pack adds to your total Volume One leaderboard score. Purchasing and completing all the Mission Packs for Volume One will earn you an extra song for the EmoRay Boombox. *This Mission Pack can only be purchased if you have purchased EmoRay  Volume One.

desc: This will change the sky in your Blueprint  Home to a blissful night time sky. Note - You must own Blueprint  Home by nDreams to use this item.

desc: Build your home in the middle of a surreal desert, what mysteries will you see? Note - You will need to own Blueprint  Home to access this content once it has been purchased.

desc: Want your apartment to look war-torn and post-apocalyptic? Then this is an essential purchase for your Blueprint  Home. desc: The perfect environment for those who do not wish to be disturbed. This environment comes complete with falling snow. Note - You must own Blueprint  Home by nDreams to use this item.

name: The Complex 2  Kitchen
desc: Purchasing this item will unlock the Kitchen area within The Complex 2.

name: Diamond Beach Mansion Second Floor
desc: Expand your Modern Beach Mansion with the second floor, complete with your Master Bedroom and Bathroom, Study and Home Theater. No modern mansion would be complete without a home theater. Bring your friends over for a private screening and gift them with exclusive freebies  Golden Robe (male and female), Gold Accented Bed, Animated Fish Tank Nightstand, and a Painting. The Second Floor of your Modern Beach Mansion adds to the interactive features with a bed you can lay in.

name: Diamond Beach Mansion First Floor
desc: Enter the most luxurious personal space in PlayStation Home. The Diamond Beach Mansion is packed with special features befitting the rich and famous - from a gifting machine that lets you give your friends exclusive virtual items (and built-in rewards for the owner) to fully-functional appliances and fun interactives like the Tropical Fish Tank game and user-controlled weather and day night cycles. This lush island paradise even includes a White Lion pet that guards your estate while you and your friends party on (til the break of dawn). Collect all four levels of the Diamond Beach Mansion to unlock a secret area.

name: Blueprint  Home - Golden Sunset Sky
desc: A beautiful sky that can be used to change the mood in your Blueprint  Home. You will need to own Blueprint  Home to access these items.

desc: EmoRay  Volume One Contents immediately available in game  -Access to Chapters 1 - 4 in Story Mode -Emos Garage Loft -Emo Ray Outfit (Male) -Emo Ray Outfit (Female) -Emo Ray Boombox with 1 Song Access to earn these rewards in game  -Porsche Outfit (Female) -Hammy Outfit (Male) -Chopper Outfit (Male) -Mr.Radd Outfit (Male) -An additional song for the Emo Ray Boombox -Cuddly Bear Head (Male) -Cuddly Bear Head (Female) -Health Pick Up (Ornament) -Ammo Pick Up (Ornament) -Spare Parts (Ornament) -Cuddly Bear Poster (Wall Hanging) -Heavy Water Poster (Wall Hanging) -Bare Cuddly Bear Chair (Chair) -Bare Cuddly Bear Rug (Flooring) -Porsche Companion -Business Man Outfit -Mailman Outfit Purchasing EmoRay  Volume One grants you the ability to post scores to leaderboards, earn ModPoints, and you receive the personal apartment  Emos Garage Loft. ModPoints can be used in EmoRay to buy weapon and vehicle upgrades as well as Virtual Items for use in PlayStation Home.
